#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; is an &irc; client built on &Qt; and &kf5-full;. It offers "
"the following features:"
msgstr ""
"&konversation; je &irc; odjemalec zgrajen na &Qt; in &kf5-full;. Ponuja "
"naslednje zmožnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "SSL support."
msgstr "SSL podpora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "User-friendly tabbed interface."
msgstr "Uporabniku prijazen vmesnik z zavihki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizable Quick Buttons for often-used commands."
msgstr "Prilagodljivi hitri gumbi za pogosto uporabljene ukaze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic reconnect and rejoin."
msgstr "Samodejna ponovna povezava in ponovna vključitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "DCC send and receive."
msgstr "DCC pošiljanje in sprejemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-Nickname; watch list."
msgstr "&i18n-Nickname; seznam spremljanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Visual and auditory notifications for a wide variety of events, such as "
"messages containing your &i18n-nickname;, or &i18n-nickname;s on your watch "
"list going online or offline."
msgstr ""
"Vizualna in zvočna obvestila o najrazličnejših dogodkih, kot so sporočila, "
"ki vsebujejo vaš &i18n-nickname; ali &i18n-nickname;e na vašem seznamu za "
"spremljanje, ki gredo v splet ali brez njega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Customizable highlighting of messages by &i18n-nickname; or regular "
"expression pattern."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodljivo označevanje sporočil od &i18n-nickname; ali po vzorcu "
"regularnega izraza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-Nickname; completion."
msgstr "&i18n-Nickname; dokončanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capture and save all &URL;s appearing in messages."
msgstr "Zajemite in shranite vse &URL;-je, ki se pojavljajo v sporočilih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "On-screen display of messages, even when minimized."
msgstr "Prikaz sporočil na zaslonu tudi ko je minimiziran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-Nickname; ignore list."
msgstr "&i18n-Nickname; seznam prezrtih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic logging and log management."
msgstr "Samodejno beleženje in upravljanje dnevnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Marking of lines in logs."
msgstr "Označevanje vrstic v dnevnikih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting."
msgstr "Skriptiranje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &konversation; website is <ulink url=\"&konviwebsite;\">&konviwebsite;</"
"ulink>. Further information like a FAQ and tips and tricks you find in the "
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Konversation\">&konversation; UserBase "
"page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&konversation; spletno mesto je <ulink url=\"&konviwebsite;\">&konviwebsite;"
"</ulink>. Dodatne informacije, kot so pogosta vprašanja ter nasveti in "
"triki, najdete v <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Konversation\">stran "
"&konversation; UserBase</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Developers for &konversation; can often be contacted via &irc; at <ulink url="
"\"irc://irc.libera.chat/konversation\">irc.libera.chat channel "
"#konversation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Razvijalci za &konversation; z njimi lahko pogosto stopite v stik prek &irc; "
"na <ulink url=\"irc://irc.libera.chat/konversation\">kanalu irc.libera.chat "
"#konversation</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &konversation;"
msgstr "Uporaba &konversation;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you haven't used &irc; before..."
msgstr "Če še niste uporabljali &irc; prej..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply put, &irc; is a chat protocol, defined by official Internet "
"standards, and capable of stealing many hours of your life. To use &irc;, "
"you must connect to a server, and then join a channel (equivalent to a chat "
"room) or just engage in private conversations."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto povedano, &irc; je protokol za klepet, ki ga določajo uradni "
"internetni standardi in vam lahko ukrade veliko ur življenja. Če želite "
"uporabljati &irc;, se morate povezati s strežnikom in se nato pridružiti "
"kanalu (enakovredno klepetalnici) ali samo sodelovati v zasebnih pogovorih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To connect to a server and channel, open &konversation;. The "
"<guilabel>Server List</guilabel> screen appears."
msgstr ""
"Za povezavo s strežnikom in kanalom odprite &konversation;. Prikaže se "
"zaslon <guilabel>Seznam strežnikov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:215 index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Server List</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Seznam strežnikov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:228 index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Server List</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Seznam strežnikov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of configured &irc; <guilabel>Networks</guilabel> are listed here. "
"An &irc; network is a collection of cooperating servers. You need only "
"connect to one of the servers in the network to be connected to the entire "
"&irc; network. Once connected, &konversation; will automatically join the "
"<guilabel>Channels</guilabel> shown. When &konversation; is started for the "
"first time, the <userinput><replaceable>Libera</replaceable></userinput> "
"network and <userinput><replaceable>#kde</replaceable></userinput> channel "
"are already entered for you. Click on a network to select it."
msgstr ""
"Seznam konfiguriranih &irc; <guilabel>Omrežja</guilabel> so navedena tukaj. "
"&irc; omrežje je zbirka sodelujočih strežnikov. Povezati se morate z enim od "
"strežnikov, če želite biti povezani s celotnim &irc; omrežjem. Ko je "
"vzpostavljena povezava, se bo &konversation; samodejno pridružil prikazanim "
"<guilabel>kanalom</guilabel>. Ko &konversation; zaženete prvič, sta omrežje "
"<userinput><replaceable>Libera</replaceable></userinput> in kanal "
"<userinput><replaceable>#kde</replaceable></userinput> že vnesena. Kliknite "
"na omrežje, da ga izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to define a new <guilabel>Network</guilabel>, including the "
"server to connect to, and the <guilabel>Channels</guilabel> to automatically "
"join once connected. See <link linkend=\"serverlist\">Defining new networks, "
"servers, and auto join channels</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da določite novo <guilabel>Omrežje</guilabel>, vključno s "
"strežnikom za povezavo in <guilabel>Kanali</guilabel>, ki se jim samodejno "
"pridružite, ko se vzpostavi povezava. Glejte <link linkend=\"serverlist"
"\">Določanje novih omrežij, strežnikov in kanalov za samodejno pridružitev</"
"link> za več informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to connect to the selected &irc; network and channel."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj za povezavo z izbranim &irc; omrežjem in kanalom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guibutton>Connect</guibutton> button the first time you "
"open &konversation;, you may see the following message, telling you that "
"your default <guilabel>identity</guilabel> is not set up correctly."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Poveži</guibutton>, ko prvič odprete "
"&konversation;, boste morda videli naslednje sporočilo, ki vam pove, da vaša "
"privzeta <guilabel>identiteta</guilabel> ni pravilno nastavljena."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Check Identities</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Preveri identitete</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Check Identities</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Preveri identitete</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first time you open &konversation; it obtains information about the "
"current user from the operating system and fills in defaults for the "
"Identity. If the operating system user information is not complete, for "
"example, no Full Name is defined, you may see the message above. To correct "
"this problem, click <guibutton>Edit Identity...</guibutton> and see <link "
"linkend=\"identity\">Setting your identity</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič odprete &konversation; od operacijskega sistema pridobi informacije "
"o trenutnem uporabniku in izpolni privzete vrednosti za Identiteto. Če "
"podatki o uporabniku operacijskega sistema niso popolni, na primer ni "
"definirano polno ime, boste morda videli zgornje sporočilo. Če želite "
"odpraviti to težavo, kliknite <guibutton>Uredi identiteto...</guibutton> in "
"glejte <link linkend=\"identity\">Nastavitev vaše identitete</link> za več "
"informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Main</interface> screen will be displayed showing the "
"messages sent by the server to the client. (If &konversation; will not "
"connect to the server, see <link linkend=\"faq\">Questions and Answers</"
"link>.) When the server messages have finished scrolling past, "
"&konversation; will join the channel or channels chosen."
msgstr ""
"Prikazal se bo <interface>Glavni</interface> zaslon, ki prikazuje sporočila, "
"ki jih je strežnik poslal odjemalcu. (Če se &konversation; ne poveže s "
"strežnikom, glejte <link linkend=\"faq\">Vprašanja in odgovori</link>.) Ko "
"se sporočila strežnika končajo, se &konversation; se bo pridružil izbranemu "
"kanalu ali kanalom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Channel."
msgstr "Kanal."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Channel</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kanal</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is called the <interface>Input Line</interface>. To send a message to "
"everyone in the channel, type the message here and press &Enter;. Your "
"message, as well as everyone else's messages appear in the channel scroll "
"above. Each message is preceded by the time and the user's &i18n-nickname;."
msgstr ""
"To se imenuje <interface>Vhodna vrstica</interface>. Če želite poslati "
"vsakomu vsem v kanalu, vnesite sporočilo tukaj in pritisnite &Enter;. Vaše "
"sporočilo in sporočila vseh ostalih se prikažejo v zgornjem drsniku kanalov. "
"Pred vsakim sporočilom sta čas in uporabnikov &i18n-nickname;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may join additional servers and channels. Each server, channel, channel "
"list, and other screen gets a separate tab here. To display a list of "
"available channels, see <link linkend=\"list-channels\">Listing available "
"channels</link>. To join a channel, type: <userinput><command>/join</"
"command> <replaceable>#channelname</replaceable></userinput> in the Input "
"Line. (The <userinput>#</userinput> is required.) You may also type "
"<userinput><command>/j</command></userinput> as a shorthand to "
"<userinput><command>/join</command></userinput>. To leave a channel, just "
"type <userinput><command>/part</command></userinput>. To switch the display "
"to a different server or channel, click the corresponding tab."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se pridružite dodatnim strežnikom in kanalom. Vsak strežnik, kanal, "
"seznam kanalov in drugi zasloni tukaj dobijo ločen zavihek. Če želite "
"prikazati seznam razpoložljivih kanalov, glejte <link linkend=\"list-channels"
"\">Prikaz razpoložljivih kanalov</link>. Če se želite pridružiti kanalu, "
"vnesite: <userinput><command>/join</command> <replaceable>#channelname</"
"replaceable></userinput> v vnosno vrstico. (Potreben je <userinput>#</"
"userinput>.) Vnesete lahko tudi <userinput><command>/j</command></userinput> "
"kot okrajšavo za <userinput><command>/join</command> </userinput>. Če želite "
"zapustiti kanal, vnesite <userinput><command>/part</command></userinput>. Če "
"želite zaslon preklopiti na drug strežnik ali kanal, kliknite ustrezen "
"zavihek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is called the <interface>Nick Panel</interface>. It lists the &i18n-"
"nickname;s of all the users who have joined the channel, including yourself."
msgstr ""
"To se imenuje <interface>Plošča vzdevkov</interface>. V njem so navedeni "
"vzdevki vseh uporabnikov, ki so se pridružili kanalu, vključno z vami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "That's the basics, for more detailed information, read on..."
msgstr "To je osnova, za podrobnejše informacije berite dalje..."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting your identity"
msgstr "Nastavitev vaše identitete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before you start using &konversation; regularly, you should set how you will "
"be identified on the network."
msgstr ""
"Preden začnete uporabljati &konversation; redno morate nastaviti, kako boste "
"prepoznani v omrežju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Identities</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The "
"<guilabel>Identities</guilabel> screen will appear. You can also display the "
"<guilabel>Identities</guilabel> screen by clicking the <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> button on the <guilabel>Edit Network</guilabel> or <guilabel>New "
"Network</guilabel> screen.</action>"
msgstr ""
"V glavnem meniju kliknite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Identitete</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. <action>Pojavil se bo "
"zaslon <guilabel>Identitete</guilabel>. Zaslon <guilabel>Identitete</"
"guilabel> lahko prikažete tudi tako, da kliknete gumb <guibutton>Uredi</"
"guibutton> na zaslonu <guilabel>Uredi omrežje</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Novo "
"omrežje</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identities (General tab)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Identitete (zavihek Splošno)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identities (General tab)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Identitete (zavihek Splošno)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to select an <guilabel>Identity</guilabel> to edit."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da izberete <guilabel>Identiteto</guilabel> za urejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these buttons to <guibutton>Add</guibutton>, <guibutton>Duplicate</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Rename</guibutton>, or <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> "
"an <guilabel>Identity</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"S temi gumbi <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>, <guibutton>Podvoji</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>Preimenuj</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton> "
"<guilabel>Identitete</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter your real name here. &irc; is not intended to keep you hidden from "
"your friends or enemies. Keep this in mind if you are tempted to behave "
"maliciously. A fake \"real name\" can be a good way to mask your gender from "
"all the nerds out there, but the PC you use can always be traced so you will "
"never be truly anonymous."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite svoje pravo ime. &irc; ni namenjen temu, da bi vas skrili pred "
"prijatelji ali sovražniki. Imejte to v mislih, če vas mika, da bi se "
"obnašali zlonamerno. Lažno \"pravo ime\" je lahko dober način, da prikrijete "
"svoj spol pred vsemi čudaki, vendar je računalnik, ki ga uporabljate, vedno "
"mogoče izslediti, tako da nikoli ne boste zares anonimni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these buttons to <guibutton>Add</guibutton> or <guibutton>Remove</"
"guibutton> a &i18n-nickname;."
msgstr ""
"S temi gumbi <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Odstrani</"
"guibutton> &i18n-nickname;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is your list of &i18n-nickname;s. A &i18n-nickname; is the name that "
"other users will know you by. You may use any name you desire. The first "
"character must be a letter. Other characters may be letters, numbers, or the "
"special characters <literal>-[]\\`_^{}|</literal>."
msgstr ""
"To je vaš seznam &i18n-Nickname;-ov . &i18n-nickname; je ime, po katerem vas "
"bodo drugi uporabniki poznali. Uporabite lahko poljubno ime. Prvi znak mora "
"biti črka. Drugi znaki so lahko črke, številke ali posebni znaki <literal>-"
"[]\\\\`_^{}|</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &i18n-nickname;s must be unique across an entire &irc; network, your "
"desired name may be rejected by the server because someone else is already "
"using that &i18n-nickname;. Enter alternate &i18n-nickname;s for yourself. "
"If your first choice is rejected by the server, &konversation; will try the "
"alternate &i18n-nickname;s."
msgstr ""
"Ker morajo biti  &i18n-nickname; edinstveni v celotnem &irc; omrežja, lahko "
"strežnik zavrne vaše želeno ime, ker nekdo drug že uporablja ta &i18n-"
"nickname;. Vnesite nadomestne vzdevke zase. Če vašo prvo izbiro strežnik "
"zavrne, bo &konversation; poskusil z nadomestnimi  &i18n-nickname;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"According to RFC 2812, the maximum &i18n-nickname; length is 9, but this is "
"actually determined by the server. To determine the maximum for a server, "
"connect to the server. In the <interface>Server Messages</interface> tab, "
"look for a <computeroutput>[Support]</computeroutput> message. For example:"
msgstr ""
"V skladu z RFC 2812 je največja dolžina &i18n-nickname; 9, vendar to "
"dejansko določi strežnik. Če želite določiti največjo vrednost za strežnik, "
"se povežite s strežnikom. V zavihku <interface>Server Messages</interface> "
"poiščite sporočilo <computeroutput>[Support]</computeroutput>. Na primer:"

#. Tag: computeroutput
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[18:51] *Eisfuchs* [21:45] [Support] Eisfuchs MODES=4 MAXCHANNELS=20 "
"NICKLEN=16 USERLEN=10 HOSTLEN=63 TOPICLEN=450 KICKLEN=450 CHANNELLEN=30 "
"KEYLEN=23 CHANTYPES=# PREFIX=@+ CASEMAPPING=ascii CAPAB IRCD=dancer"
msgstr ""
"[18:51] *Eisfuchs* [21:45] [Support] Eisfuchs MODES=4 MAXCHANNELS=20 "
"NICKLEN=16 USERLEN=10 HOSTLEN=63 TOPICLEN=450 KICKLEN=450 CHANNELLEN=30 "
"KEYLEN=23 CHANTYPES=# PREFIX=@+ CASEMAPPING=ascii CAPAB IRCD=dancer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <computeroutput>NICKLEN</computeroutput> parameter specifies the maximum "
"&i18n-nickname; length."
msgstr ""
"Parameter <computeroutput>NICKLEN</computeroutput> določa največjo dolžino "
"&i18n-nickname;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these buttons to change the order of the &i18n-nickname;s. The top &i18n-"
"nickname; is tried first, then the next &i18n-nickname;, and so on."
msgstr ""
"S temi gumbi spremenite vrstni red &i18n-nickname;. Najvišji  &i18n-nickname;"
"najprej poskusi, nato naslednji &i18n-nickname;, in tako naprej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have registered your &i18n-nickname; with the &irc; network, enter "
"the service and password to authenticate your &i18n-nickname;. When "
"&konversation; connects, it will automatically send <userinput><command>/"
"msg</command> <replaceable>service</replaceable> <command>IDENTIFY</command> "
"<replaceable>password</replaceable></userinput> to the server. If you don't "
"know what this is, leave these boxes blank."
msgstr ""
"Če ste registrirali svoj &i18n-nickname; z &irc; omrežjem, vnesite storitev "
"in geslo za preverjanje pristnosti vašega &i18n-nickname;. Ko &konversation; "
"vzpostavi povezavo, bo strežniku samodejno poslal <userinput><command>/msg</"
"command> <replaceable>service</replaceable> <command>IDENTIFY</command> "
"<replaceable>geslo</replaceable></userinput>. Če ne veste, kaj je to, "
"pustite ta polja prazna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click the <guilabel>Away</guilabel> tab."
msgstr "Kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Odsoten</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identities (Away tab)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Identitete (zavihek Odsoten)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identities (Away tab)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Identitete (zavihek Odsoten)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a &i18n-nickname; that indicates you are away. Whenever you perform an "
"<userinput><command>/away </command><replaceable>msg</replaceable></"
"userinput> command in any channel joined with this <guilabel>Identity</"
"guilabel>, &konversation; will automatically change your &i18n-nickname; to "
"the <guilabel>Away nickname</guilabel>. Other users will be able to tell you "
"are away from your computer. Whenever you perform an <userinput><command>/"
"away</command></userinput> command in any channel in which you are away, "
"&konversation; will automatically change your &i18n-nickname; back to the "
"original. If you do not wish to automatically change your &i18n-nickname; "
"when going away, leave blank."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite &i18n-nickname; ki pomeni, da ste odsotni. Kadarkoli izvedete ukaz "
"<userinput><command>/away </command><replaceable>msg</replaceable></"
"userinput> v katerem koli kanalu, ki je povezan s to <guilabel>Identiteto</"
"guilabel>, bo &konversation; samodejno spremenil vaš &i18n-nickname; na "
"<guilabel>vzdevek odsoten</guilabel>. Drugi uporabniki bodo lahko vedeli, da "
"niste pri računalniku. Kadarkoli izvedete ukaz <userinput><command>/away</"
"command></userinput> v katerem koli kanalu, v katerem ste odsotni, "
"&konversation; bo samodejno spremenil vaš &i18n-nickname; nazaj na izvirnik. "
"Če ne želite samodejno spremeniti svojega &i18n-nickname; ko ste odsotni, "
"pustite prazno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this box, whenever you perform an <userinput><command>/away</"
"command></userinput> command, a horizontal line will appear in the channel, "
"marking the point where you went away. Other &irc; users do not see this "
"horizontal line."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to polje, se bo vsakič, ko izvedete ukaz <userinput><command>/"
"away</command></userinput>, v kanalu pojavila vodoravna črta, ki označuje "
"točko, kjer ste odšli. Drugi &irc; uporabniki te vodoravne črte ne vidijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this box, &konversation; will automatically send the "
"<guilabel>Away command</guilabel> to all channels joined with this "
"<guilabel>Identity</guilabel>. <userinput><replaceable>%s</replaceable></"
"userinput> is replaced with <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></"
"userinput>. Whenever you perform an <userinput><command>/away</command></"
"userinput> command, the <guilabel>Return command</guilabel> will be "
"displayed in all channels joined with this <guilabel>Identity</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite to polje, &konversation; samodejno pošlje <guilabel>ukaz Away</"
"guilabel> vsem kanalom, ki so združeni s to <guilabel>Identiteto</guilabel>. "
"<userinput><replaceable>%s</replaceable></userinput> je nadomeščen z "
"<userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput>. Kadarkoli izvedete "
"ukaz <userinput><command>/away</command></userinput>, bo <guilabel>ukaz "
"Return</guilabel> prikazan v vseh kanalih, ki so združeni s to "
"<guilabel>Identiteto</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Away messages are often considered annoying by other users. Use this option "
"carefully, with consideration for your fellow &irc; users."
msgstr ""
"Drugi uporabniki pogosto menijo, da so sporočila o odsotnosti moteča. To "
"možnost uporabljajte previdno, upoštevajoč svoje kolege &irc; uporabnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click the <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> tab."
msgstr "Kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Identities (Advanced tab)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Identitete (zavihek Napredno)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Identities (Advanced tab)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Identitete (zavihek Napredno)</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter a command here that will be executed before connecting to the "
"server. If this identity is used for more than one server, the command will "
"be executed for each server."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vnesete ukaz, ki bo izveden pred povezavo s strežnikom. Če se ta "
"identiteta uporablja za več kot en strežnik, bo ukaz izveden za vsak "
"strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting affects how characters you type are encoded for sending to the "
"server. It also affects how messages are displayed. When you first open "
"&konversation;, it automatically retrieves this setting from the operating "
"system. If you seem to be having trouble seeing other user's messages "
"correctly, try changing this setting."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev vpliva na to, kako so znaki, ki jih vnesete, kodirani za "
"pošiljanje v strežnik. Vpliva tudi na to, kako so sporočila prikazana. Ko "
"prvič odprete &konversation;, samodejno pridobi to nastavitev iz "
"operacijskega sistema. Če se zdi, da imate težave s pravilnim ogledom "
"sporočil drugih uporabnikov, poskusite spremeniti to nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you connect, many servers query your computer for an IDENT response. If "
"your computer is not running an IDENT server, this response is sent by "
"&konversation;. No spaces are allowed. Your first name is suggested."
msgstr ""
"Ko vzpostavite povezavo, veliko strežnikov od vašega računalnika zahteva "
"odgovor IDENT. Če vaš računalnik ne izvaja strežnika IDENT, ta odgovor "
"pošlje &konversation;. Presledki niso dovoljeni. Predlagano je vaše lastno "
"ime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whenever you leave a channel, this message is sent to the channel."
msgstr "Kadarkoli zapustite kanal, se to sporočilo pošlje kanalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever you are kicked from a channel (usually by an &irc; operator), this "
"message is sent to the channel."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli vas vržejo iz kanala (običajno operater &irc;), se to sporočilo "
"pošlje kanalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click to apply your changes. In order for all the changes to take effect, "
"you must disconnect from the server and re-connect. The easiest way to do "
"that is to quit &konversation; and restart."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite, da uveljavite svoje spremembe. Da bi vse spremembe stopile v "
"veljavo, morate prekiniti povezavo s strežnikom in se znova povezati. "
"Najlažji način za to je, da zaprete &konversation; in znova zaženete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining new networks, servers and auto join channels"
msgstr ""
"Definiranje novih omrežij, strežnikov in kanalov za samodejno pridružitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Server List</guilabel> screen appears when you open the "
"&konversation; program. It also appears when you choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>File</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Server List</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The <guilabel>Server List</guilabel></"
"action> screen lists your existing defined &irc; <guilabel>Network</"
"guilabel>s, listed by group. An &irc; network is a collection of cooperating "
"servers. When you connect to any server in a network, you have access to all "
"the channels of the network. Examples of &irc; networks are "
"<userinput><replaceable>Libera</replaceable></userinput> and "
"<userinput><replaceable>Undernet</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon <guilabel>Seznam strežnikov</guilabel> se prikaže, ko odpreteprogram "
"&konversation;. Pojavi se tudi, ko izberete "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Datoteka</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Seznam strežnikov</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action><guilabel>Seznam "
"strežnikov</guilabel></action> zaslon navaja vaše obstoječe definirane &irc; "
"<guilabel>Omrežje</guilabel>s, razvrščenih po skupinah. An &irc; omrežje je "
"zbirka sodelujočihstrežnikov. Ko se povežete s katerim koli strežnikom v "
"omrežju, imate dostop do vsehkanalov omrežja. Primeri &irc; omrežja "
"so<userinput><replaceable>Libera</replaceable></userinput> "
"in<userinput><replaceable>Undernet</replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your existing defined <guilabel>Network</guilabel>s are listed here along "
"with the <guilabel>Identity</guilabel> used to connect to the network, and "
"the <guilabel>Channels</guilabel> automatically joined when connected. If "
"you have specified a group for your networks, networks are listed indented "
"under the group. Click on a network to select it."
msgstr ""
"Vaša obstoječa definirana <guilabel>omrežja</guilabel> so navedena tukaj "
"skupaj z <guilabel>identiteto</guilabel>, ki se uporablja za povezavo z "
"omrežjem, in <guilabel>kanali</guilabel>, ki se samodejno pridružijo, ko se "
"povežete. Če ste določili skupino za svoja omrežja, so omrežja navedena z "
"zamikom pod skupino. Kliknite omrežje, da ga izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these buttons to <guibutton>Add</guibutton> a new network, "
"<guibutton>Edit</guibutton> a highlighted network, or <guibutton>Delete</"
"guibutton> a highlighted network."
msgstr ""
"S temi gumbi <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> novo omrežje, <guibutton>Uredi</"
"guibutton> označeno omrežje ali <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> označeno "
"omrežje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to connect to the highlighted <guilabel>Network</guilabel> "
"and close the <guilabel>Server List</guilabel> screen. You may highlight "
"more than one network if you wish, which will connect to all the highlighted "
"networks."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, da se povežete z označenim <guilabel>Omrežjem</guilabel> "
"in zaprete zaslon <guilabel>Seznam strežnikov</guilabel>. Če želite, lahko "
"označite več kot eno omrežje, ki se bo povezalo z vsemi označenimi omrežji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button does not discard the changes you have made. It merely "
"means you do not wish to connect to any networks at this time."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta gumb ne zavržete sprememb, ki ste jih naredili. To samo "
"pomeni, da se trenutno ne želite povezati z nobenim omrežjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button, the <guilabel>New "
"Network</guilabel> screen appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Novo</guibutton>, se prikaže zaslon "
"<guilabel>Novo omrežje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New Network</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novo omrežje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New Network</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Novo omrežje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the <guilabel>Network name</guilabel> here. You may create as many "
"entries in the <guilabel>Server List</guilabel> screen with the same "
"<guilabel>Network</guilabel> as you like."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite <guilabel>Ime omrežja</guilabel>. Ustvarite lahko toliko "
"vnosov na zaslonu <guilabel>Seznam strežnikov</guilabel> z istim "
"<guilabel>Omrežjem</guilabel>, kot želite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose an existing <guilabel>Identity</guilabel> or click the "
"<guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button to add a new Identity or edit an existing "
"one. The <guilabel>Identity</guilabel> will identify you and determine your "
"&i18n-nickname; when you connect to the network."
msgstr ""
"Izberite obstoječo <guilabel>Identiteto</guilabel> ali kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>, da dodate novo identiteto ali uredite "
"obstoječo. <guilabel>Identiteta</guilabel> vas bo identificirala in določila "
"vaš  &i18n-nickname; ko se povežete z omrežjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optional. This command will be sent to the server after connecting. Example: "
"<userinput>/msg NickServ IDENTIFY <replaceable>konvirocks</replaceable></"
"userinput>. This example is for the Libera network, which requires users to "
"register their &i18n-nickname; with a password and login when connecting. "
"<userinput><replaceable>konvirocks</replaceable></userinput> is the password "
"for the &i18n-nickname; given in <guilabel>Identity</guilabel>. You may "
"enter more than one command by separating them with semicolons."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezno. Ta ukaz bo poslan strežniku po vzpostavitvi povezave. Primer: "
"<userinput>/msg NickServ IDENTIFY <replaceable>konvirocks</replaceable></"
"userinput>. Ta primer je za omrežje Libera, ki od uporabnikov zahteva, da "
"registrirajo svoj &i18n-nickname; z geslom in prijavo ob povezovanju. "
"<userinput><replaceable>konvirocks</replaceable></userinput> je geslo za "
"&i18n-nickname; podan v <guilabel>Identiteta</guilabel>. Vnesete lahko več "
"kot en ukaz, tako da jih ločite s podpičji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check here if you want &konversation; to automatically connect to this "
"network whenever you open &konversation;."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj označite, če želite &konversation; da se samodejno poveže s tem "
"omrežjem vsakič, ko odprete &konversation;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of &irc; <guilabel>Servers</guilabel> in the network. When "
"connecting to the network, &konversation; will attempt to connect to the top "
"server first. If this fails, it will attempt the second server. If this "
"fails, it will attempt the third, and so on. At least one server must be "
"specified. Click a server to highlight it."
msgstr ""
"To je seznam &irc; <guilabel>Strežniki</guilabel> v omrežju. Ko se povežete "
"z omrežjem, &konversation; se bo najprej poskusil povezati z zgornjim "
"strežnikom. Če to ne uspe, bo poskusil z drugim strežnikom. Če to ne uspe, "
"bo poskusil tretjega in tako naprej. Določen mora biti vsaj en strežnik. "
"Kliknite strežnik, da ga označite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these buttons to <guibutton>Add</guibutton> a server, <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> a highlighted server, or <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> a "
"highlighted server. You can also adjust the order of the server list and "
"therefore the order of connection attempts."
msgstr ""
"S temi gumbi <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> strežnik, <guibutton>Uredi</"
"guibutton> označeni strežnik ali <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> označeni "
"strežnik. Prilagodite lahko tudi vrstni red seznama strežnikov in s tem "
"vrstni red poskusov povezave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optional. This is a list of the channels that will be automatically joined "
"once &konversation; has connected to a server. You may leave this blank if "
"you wish to not automatically join any channels."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezno. To je seznam kanalov, ki se bodo samodejno pridružili, ko se bo "
"&konversation; povezal s strežnikom. To lahko pustite prazno, če se ne "
"želite samodejno pridružiti nobenemu kanalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these buttons to <guibutton>Add</guibutton> a channel, <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> a highlighted channel, or <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> a "
"highlighted channel. You may also change the order the channels are joined."
msgstr ""
"S temi gumbi <guibutton>Dodajte</guibutton> kanal, <guibutton>Uredite</"
"guibutton> označeni kanal ali <guibutton>Izbrišete</guibutton> označeni "
"kanal. Prav tako lahko spremenite vrstni red združevanja kanalov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Avoid mixing servers on different &irc; networks under the same "
"<guilabel>Network</guilabel>. Avoid entering the same server under two "
"different <guilabel>Network</guilabel>s. Otherwise, <link linkend="
"\"nicksonline\">monitoring of online &i18n-nickname;s</link> will not "
"function correctly."
msgstr ""
"Izogibajte se mešanju strežnikov na različnih &irc; omrežjih pod istim "
"<guilabel>Omrežjem</guilabel>. Izogibajte se vstopu v isti strežnik pod "
"dvema različnima <guilabel>omrežjema</guilabel>. V nasprotnem primeru <link "
"linkend=\"nicksonline\">spremljanje spletnih &i18n-nickname;-ov</link> ne bo "
"delovalo pravilno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button in the "
"<guilabel>Servers</guilabel> frame, the <guilabel>Add Server</guilabel> "
"screen appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> v okviru <guilabel>Strežniki</"
"guilabel>, se prikaže zaslon <guilabel>Dodaj strežnik</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Add Server</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodaj strežnik</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Add Server</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodaj strežnik</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name or IP number of the server. irchelp.org maintains a <ulink url="
"\"https://www.irchelp.org/networks/\">list</ulink> of servers."
msgstr ""
"Ime ali številka IP strežnika. irchelp.org vzdržuje <ulink url=\"https://www."
"irchelp.org/networks/\">seznam</ulink> strežnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the port number required to connect to the server. For most servers, "
"this should be <userinput>6667</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite številko vrat, potrebnih za povezavo s strežnikom. Za večino "
"strežnikov bi to moralo biti <userinput>6667</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the server requires a password in order to connect, enter it here, "
"otherwise leave blank."
msgstr ""
"Če strežnik zahteva geslo za povezavo, ga vnesite tukaj, sicer pustite "
"prazno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check if you want to use Secure Socket Layer (SSL) protocol to communicate "
"with the server. This protects the privacy of your communications between "
"your computer and the &irc; server. The server must support SSL protocol for "
"this to work. In most cases, if the server does not support SSL, the "
"connection will fail."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, ali želite za komunikacijo s strežnikom uporabljati protokol SSL "
"(Secure Socket Layer). To ščiti zasebnost vaše komunikacije med vašim "
"računalnikom in &irc; strežnik. Strežnik mora podpirati protokol SSL, da to "
"deluje. V večini primerov povezava ne bo uspela, če strežnik ne podpira SSL."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button in the <guilabel>Auto "
"Join Channels</guilabel> frame, the <guilabel>Add Channel</guilabel> screen "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> v okviru <guilabel>Samodejna "
"pridružitev kanalom</guilabel>, se prikaže zaslon <guilabel>Dodaj kanal</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Add Channel</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodaj kanal</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Add Channel</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodaj kanal</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a channel name. Do not forget leading <userinput><replaceable>#</"
"replaceable></userinput>. If the channel requires a password in order to "
"join, enter it, otherwise leave blank."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ime kanala. Ne pozabite na začetni <userinput><replaceable>#</"
"replaceable></userinput>. Če kanal zahteva geslo za pridružitev, ga vnesite, "
"sicer pustite prazno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Listing available channels"
msgstr "Prikaz razpoložljivih kanalov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display a list of available channels, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Channel List</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>After a warning screen, a new tab is "
"created called the <guilabel>Channel List</guilabel>.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz seznama razpoložljivih kanalov izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Okno</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Seznam kanalov</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Po opozorilnem zaslonu se ustvari nov "
"zavihek, imenovan <guilabel>Seznam kanalov</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Channel List tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zavihek Seznam kanalov.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Channel List tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihek Seznam kanalov.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a filter string here."
msgstr "Tukaj vnesite niz filtra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can limit the channel list to those channels with a minimum or maximum "
"number of users here. Choosing <guilabel>No Limit</guilabel> disables the "
"respective criteria."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko seznam kanalov omejite na tiste kanale z najmanjšim ali "
"največjim številom uporabnikov. Če izberete <guilabel>Brez omejitev</"
"guilabel>, onemogočite ustrezne kriterije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to retrieve the list of channels from the server and apply the "
"filter."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da pridobite seznam kanalov s strežnika in uporabite filter."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filtered list of channels is displayed here. Notice that if you don't "
"use regular expressions, &konversation; lists any channel whose name "
"contains the filter string you entered. The channel name does not have to "
"start with the string you entered."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je prikazan filtriran seznam kanalov. Upoštevajte, da če ne "
"uporabljate regularnih izrazov, &konversation; prikaže vse kanale, katerih "
"ime vsebuje niz filtra, ki ste ga vnesli. Ni nujno, da se ime kanala začne z "
"nizom, ki ste ga vnesli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a channel you want to join by clicking on it. Right click on the "
"channel to get a list of all web addresses mentioned in the channel's topic."
msgstr ""
"Izberite kanal, ki se mu želite pridružiti, tako da ga kliknete. Desni klik "
"na kanal, da dobite seznam vseh spletnih naslovov, omenjenih v temi kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to join the channel. A new tab is created for the channel."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da se pridružite kanalu. Za kanal je ustvarjen nov zavihek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes there are \"secret\" channels on servers. Such channels are not "
"listed in the <guilabel>Channel List</guilabel>. You can still join these "
"channels if you know their name. In any <interface>Input Line</interface>, "
"type: <userinput><command>/join</command> <replaceable>#channelname</"
"replaceable></userinput>. (The <userinput>#</userinput> is required.) A new "
"tab is created for the channel. If you join a channel and the Nick Panel "
"lists only your &i18n-nickname;, it means that the channel did not exist "
"before. The server created the channel and you are the operator. In this "
"case, you probably want to close the channel by typing: <userinput><command>/"
"part</command></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Včasih so na strežnikih \"skrivni\" kanali. Takšni kanali niso navedeni na "
"<guilabel>Seznamu kanalov</guilabel>. Še vedno se lahko pridružite tem "
"kanalom, če poznate njihovo ime. V katero koli <interface>Vnosno vrstico</"
"interface> vnesite: <userinput><command>/join</command> "
"<replaceable>#channelname</replaceable></userinput>. (Potreben je "
"<userinput>#</userinput>.) Za kanal je ustvarjen nov zavihek. Če se "
"pridružite kanalu in je na plošči z vzdevki prikazan samo vaš &i18n-"
"nickname;, to pomeni, da kanal prej ni obstajal. Strežnik je ustvaril kanal "
"in vi ste operater. V tem primeru boste verjetno želeli kanal zapreti tako, "
"da vnesete: <userinput><command>/part</command></userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "A tour of the main screen"
msgstr "Predstavitev glavnega zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's learn more about the <interface>Main</interface> screen. The screen is "
"shown below with a channel tab selected."
msgstr ""
"Naučimo se več o <interface>glavnem</interface> zaslonu. Spodaj je prikazan "
"zaslon z izbranim zavihkom kanala."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main screen."
msgstr "Glavni zaslon."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main screen"
msgstr "Glavni zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is called the <interface>Input Line</interface>. It appears only when "
"the current tab is a channel. To send a message to everyone in the channel, "
"type the message here and press &Enter;. Your message, as well as everyone "
"else's messages appear in the channel scroll above. Each message is preceded "
"by the time and the user's &i18n-nickname;."
msgstr ""
"To se imenuje <interface>Vhodna vrstica</interface>. Pojavi se le, če je "
"trenutni zavihek kanal. Če želite poslati sporočilo vsakomur v kanalu, "
"vnesite sporočilo tukaj in pritisnite &Enter;. Vaše sporočilo in sporočila "
"vseh ostalih se prikažejo v zgornjem drsniku kanalov. Pred vsakim sporočilom "
"sta čas in uporabnikov &i18n-nickname;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also paste text from the clipboard. If the pasted text has more than "
"one line (newlines), a dialog box appears. Edit the text as desired and "
"click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko prilepite besedilo iz odložišča. Če ima prilepljeno besedilo "
"več kot eno vrstico (nove vrstice), se prikaže pogovorno okno. Uredite "
"besedilo po želji in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the pasted text is longer than 256 characters, or it contains more than "
"one line, a warning message appears advising you that large postings can "
"cause connection resets and flooding. You can still proceed with the input, "
"but doing so is a bad idea, as flooding will annoy other users in the "
"channel, or you may be disconnected from the server. It is better to send "
"the message in shorter chunks."
msgstr ""
"Če je prilepljeno besedilo daljše od 256 znakov ali vsebuje več kot eno "
"vrstico, se prikaže opozorilo, ki vas obvešča, da lahko velike objave "
"povzročijo ponastavitev povezave in poplavo. Še vedno lahko nadaljujete z "
"vnosom, vendar je to slaba ideja, saj bo poplavljanje motilo druge "
"uporabnike v kanalu ali pa boste morda odklopljeni od strežnika. Bolje je "
"poslati sporočilo v krajših delih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A convention used in many channels is to precede messages directed at one "
"user with their &i18n-nickname;. &konversation; provides a convenient &i18n-"
"nickname; completion feature. Start typing the user's &i18n-nickname;, then "
"press &Tab;. &konversation; will complete the rest of the user's &i18n-"
"nickname; followed by a colon. To customize the completion feature, choose "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> from the main menu, expand "
"<guilabel>Behavior</guilabel>, click on <guilabel>General</guilabel>, and "
"select a <guilabel>Completion mode</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Konvencija, ki se uporablja v mnogih kanalih, je, da se pred sporočili, "
"namenjenimi enemu uporabniku, doda njihov &i18n-nickname;. &konversation; "
"ponuja priročen &i18n-nickname; s funkcijo dokončanja. Začnite vnašati "
"uporabnikov &i18n-nickname;, nato pritisnite &Tab;. &konversation; bo "
"dopolnil preostali del uporabnikovega &i18n-nickname; sledi dvopičje. Če "
"želite prilagoditi funkcijo dokončanja, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju, razširite <guilabel>Vedenje</"
"guilabel>, kliknite <guilabel >Splošno</guilabel> in izberite "
"<guilabel>Način dokončanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also enter an &irc; command here by first typing "
"<userinput><command>/</command></userinput> followed by a valid &irc; "
"command. See <link linkend=\"irc-cmds\">Frequently-used &irc; commands</"
"link>. On some servers, you can type <userinput><command>/help</command></"
"userinput> for a list of available commands, or type <userinput><command>/"
"help </command><replaceable>command</replaceable></userinput> for help on a "
"specific command."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko tudi &irc; ukaz tukaj tako, da najprej vnesete "
"<userinput><command>/</command></userinput>, ki mu sledi veljaven &irc; "
"ukaz. Glejte <link linkend=\"irc-cmds\">Pogosto uporabljeni ukazi &irc;</"
"link>. Na nekaterih strežnikih lahko vnesete <userinput><command>/help</"
"command></userinput> za seznam razpoložljivih ukazov ali "
"<userinput><command>/help </command><replaceable>command</replaceable></"
"userinput> za pomoč pri določenem ukazu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may join additional servers and channels. Each server and each channel "
"gets a separate tab here. To display a list of available channels, see <link "
"linkend=\"list-channels\">Listing available channels</link>. To join a "
"channel, type: <userinput><command>/join</command> "
"<replaceable>#channelname</replaceable></userinput> in the Input Line. (The "
"<userinput>#</userinput> is required.) To leave a channel, just type "
"<userinput><command>/part</command></userinput>. Tabs also appear here if "
"you open a <link linkend=\"list-channels\">Channel List</link>, participate "
"in a <link linkend=\"query\">private conversation (query)</link>, open the "
"<link linkend=\"urlcatcher\">&URL; Catcher</link>, or open one or more "
"<guilabel>Konsole</guilabel>s. To switch the display to a different screen, "
"click the corresponding tab, or use the mouse wheel to cycle through the "
"tabs."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se pridružite dodatnim strežnikom in kanalom. Vsak strežnik in vsak "
"kanal tukaj dobi ločen zavihek. Če želite prikazati seznam razpoložljivih "
"kanalov, glejte <link linkend=\"list-channels\">Prikaz razpoložljivih "
"kanalov</link>. Če se želite pridružiti kanalu, vnesite: "
"<userinput><command>/join</command> <replaceable>#channelname</replaceable></"
"userinput> v vnosno vrstico. (Potreben je <userinput>#</userinput>.) Če "
"želite zapustiti kanal, preprosto vnesite <userinput><command>/part</"
"command></userinput>. Zavihki se tukaj prikažejo tudi, če odprete <link "
"linkend=\"list-channels\">Seznam kanalov</link>, sodelujete v <link linkend="
"\"query\">zasebnem pogovoru (poizvedbi)</link>, odprete <link linkend="
"\"urlcatcher\">&URL; Catcher</link> ali odprite eno ali več "
"<guilabel>Konzol</guilabel>. Če želite zaslon preklopiti na drug zaslon, "
"kliknite ustrezen zavihek ali uporabite kolesce miške, da se premikate po "
"zavihkih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set other options for tabs, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> "
"from the main menu, expand <guilabel>Interface</guilabel>, click on "
"<guilabel>Tabs</guilabel> or expand <guilabel>Notifications</guilabel> and "
"click on <guilabel>Tabs</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti druge možnosti za zavihke, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju, razširite <guilabel>Vmesnik</"
"guilabel>, kliknite <guilabel>Zavihki</guilabel> ali razširite "
"<guilabel>Obvestila</guilabel> in kliknite <guilabel>Zavihki</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These &led;s will blink when there is something you haven't seen in that "
"tab. The &led; will blink slower when the only unseen messages are "
"<command>join</command>, <command>part</command>, <command>quit</command>, "
"or &i18n-nickname; changes. They blink faster if there are unseen regular "
"messages. The colors are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Te diode &led; bodo utripale, ko bo na tem zavihku nekaj, česar še niste "
"videli. &led; utripa počasneje, ko so edina še ne videna sporočila "
"<command>join</command>, <command>part</command>, <command>quit</command> "
"ali &i18n-nickname; spremembe. Hitreje utripajo, če so redna še ne videna "
"sporočila. Barve so naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Channel</para>"
msgstr "<para>Kanal</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<interface>Server Messages</interface>, <link linkend=\"list-channels"
"\">Channel List</link>, or <link linkend=\"urlcatcher\">&URL; catcher</link>."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Sporočila strežnika</interface>, <link linkend=\"list-channels"
"\">Seznam kanalov</link> ali <link linkend=\"urlcatcher\">&URL; lovilnik</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Konsole</guilabel> or <link linkend=\"dcc\">DCC Status</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Konzola</guilabel> ali <link linkend=\"dcc\">Status DCC</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"query\">Private Message (Query)</link>."
msgstr "<link linkend=\"query\">Zasebno sporočilo (poizvedba)</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to close the current tab. Closing a <interface>Channel</"
"interface> tab will leave the channel. Closing a <interface>Server Messages</"
"interface> tab will leave all channels you've joined, close all open queries "
"at that server and disconnect from the server."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da zaprete trenutni zavihek. Če zaprete zavihek "
"<interface>Kanal</interface>, boste zapustili kanal. Če zaprete zavihek "
"<interface>Sporočila strežnika</interface>, boste zapustili vse kanale, ki "
"ste se jim pridružili, zaprli vse odprte poizvedbe na tem strežniku in "
"prekinili povezavo s strežnikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to change your own &i18n-nickname;. It appears only when "
"the current tab is a channel. To hide this button, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> from the main menu, expand <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel>, click on <guilabel>Chat Window</guilabel>, and uncheck "
"<guilabel>Show box to change own nickname</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, če želite spremeniti svoj &i18n-nickname;. Pojavi se le, "
"če je trenutni zavihek kanal. Če želite skriti ta gumb, izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju, razširite "
"<guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel>, kliknite <guilabel> Okno za klepet</guilabel> "
"in počistite polje <guilabel>Pokaži polje za spremembo lastnega vzdevka</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The channel topic is displayed here. Hover the mouse over the topic to see "
"long topics. You can change the topic by clicking the button to the left of "
"the topic. To hide channel topics, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> "
"from the main menu, expand <guilabel>Interface</guilabel>, click on "
"<guilabel>Chat Window</guilabel>, and uncheck the <guilabel>Show channel "
"topic</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je prikazana tema kanala. Če želite videti dolge teme, premaknite "
"miško nad temo. Temo lahko spremenite s klikom na gumb levo od teme. Če "
"želite skriti teme kanala, izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> "
"v glavnem meniju, razširite <guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel>, kliknite "
"<guilabel> Okno za klepet</guilabel> in počistite polje <guilabel>Pokaži "
"temo kanala</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These buttons display the current state of channel modes. A button is down "
"if that mode is on. If you have the correct privileges, you can also change "
"channel modes by clicking on these buttons, or click the button to the left "
"of the topic. To hide channel mode buttons, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> from the main menu, expand <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel>, click on <guilabel>Chat Window</guilabel>, and uncheck the "
"<guilabel>Show channel mode buttons</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Ti gumbi prikazujejo trenutno stanje kanalskih načinov. Gumb je spuščen, če "
"je ta način vklopljen. Če imate ustrezne privilegije, lahko tudi spremenite "
"načine kanala s klikom na te gumbe ali pa kliknete gumb na levi strani teme. "
"Če želite skriti gumbe kanalskega načina, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju, razširite <guilabel>Vmesnik</"
"guilabel>, kliknite <guilabel >Okno za klepet</guilabel> in počistite polje "
"<guilabel>Pokaži gumbe načina kanala</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is called the <interface>Nick Panel</interface>. It is displayed "
"whenever the current tab is a channel. It lists the &i18n-nickname;s of all "
"the users who have joined the channel, including yourself. Hover the mouse "
"pointer over a &i18n-nickname; to display additional information about the "
"user. You may change how the icons are displayed next to each &i18n-"
"nickname; by changing the &i18n-nickname; icon theme. See <link linkend="
"\"nickthemes\">Configuring &i18n-nickname; themes</link> for more "
"information. The <guilabel>Default Theme</guilabel>, as shown in the screen "
"above, uses the following icons:"
msgstr ""
"To se imenuje <interface>Plošča vzdevkov</interface>. Prikaže se, kadar je "
"trenutni zavihek kanal. V njem so navedeni vzdevki vseh uporabnikov, ki so "
"se pridružili kanalu, vključno z vami. Kazalec miške premaknite nad &i18n-"
"nickname; za prikaz dodatnih informacij o uporabniku. Spremenite lahko, kako "
"so ikone prikazane poleg vsakega  &i18n-nickname; spremembo  &i18n-nickname;"
"tema ikon. Glejte <link linkend=\"nickthemes\">Konfiguriranje &i18n-"
"nickname; teme</link> za več informacij. <guilabel>Privzeta tema</guilabel>, "
"kot je prikazano na zgornjem zaslonu, uporablja naslednje ikone:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid "normal user"
msgstr "običajni uporabnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:998
#, no-c-format
msgid "voiced user. User may talk in a moderated channel."
msgstr "glasovni uporabnik. Uporabnik lahko govori v moderiranem kanalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "channel halfop"
msgstr "kanal halfop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid "channel operator"
msgstr "operater kanala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "channel owner"
msgstr "lastnik kanala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "channel admin"
msgstr "skrbnik kanala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition, if a user is away, a small clock will be drawn in the corner of "
"the icon."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega, če je uporabnik odsoten, bo v kotu ikone narisana majhna ura."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click with the &RMB; on any &i18n-nickname; to display a context menu of "
"operations you can perform with that &i18n-nickname;. For example, you can "
"<link linkend=\"dcc\">send a file</link> to the &i18n-nickname;."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite z &RMB; na katerem koli  &i18n-nickname; za prikaz kontekstnega "
"menija operacij, ki jih lahko izvedete s tem  &i18n-nickname;. Na primer, "
"lahko <link linkend=\"dcc\">pošljete datoteko</link> na &i18n-nickname;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1038
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To hide the <interface>Nick Panel</interface>, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Show Nicklist</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite skriti <interface>Ploščo vzdevkov</interface>, v glavnem meniju "
"izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Pokaži "
"seznam vzdevkov</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are called the <interface>Quick Buttons</interface>. By default, they "
"are not shown. To display them, see <link linkend=\"quick-buttons"
"\">Configuring Quick Buttons</link>. You can customize their definitions to "
"whatever commands you wish."
msgstr ""
"Ti se imenujejo <interface>hitri gumbi</interface>. Privzeto niso prikazani. "
"Če jih želite prikazati, glejte <link linkend=\"quick-buttons"
"\">Konfiguriranje hitrih gumbov</link>. Njihove definicije lahko prilagodite "
"poljubnim ukazom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control how messages are displayed in the message scroll of channel "
"and query tabs. For example, you can change the color of messages, play a "
"sound when a message containing a string is received, or automatically reply "
"to messages. See <link linkend=\"highlighting\"> Message highlighting</link> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"Nadzirate lahko, kako so sporočila prikazana v drsenju sporočil na zavihkih "
"kanala in poizvedbe. Spremenite lahko na primer barvo sporočil, predvajate "
"zvok, ko prejmete sporočilo, ki vsebuje niz, ali samodejno odgovorite na "
"sporočila. Za več informacij glejte <link linkend=\"highlighting\"> "
"Označevanje sporočil</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Channel names sometimes begin with <userinput>&amp;</userinput>, "
"<userinput>&plus;</userinput>, or <userinput>!</userinput>. The first "
"character of a channel name determines the type of channel (RFC 2811) as "
"follows: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para> <userinput>#</userinput> - Regular "
"channels. </para></listitem> <listitem><para> <userinput>!</userinput> - "
"Regular channels. </para></listitem> <listitem><para> <userinput>&amp;</"
"userinput> - Local. Channels that can only be joined from the server hosting "
"the channel. All other channels can be joined from any server in the "
"network. </para></listitem> <listitem><para> <userinput>&plus;</userinput> - "
"Channels that do not support channel modes. This means that all the modes "
"are unset, with the exception of the 't' channel flag which is set. </para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> Channel names are up to 50 characters long and may "
"contain any characters except for space, comma, and Ctrl-G (^G or ASCII 7)."
msgstr ""
"Imena kanalov se včasih začnejo z <userinput>&amp;</userinput>, "
"<userinput>&plus;</userinput> ali <userinput>!</userinput>. Prvi znak imena "
"kanala določa vrsto kanala (RFC 2811), kot sledi: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para> <userinput>#</userinput> - navadni kanali. </para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para> <userinput>!</userinput> - Navadni kanali. </"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para> <userinput>&amp;</userinput> – lokalno. "
"Kanali, ki se jim je mogoče pridružiti samo s strežnika, ki gosti kanal. "
"Vsem drugim kanalom se je mogoče pridružiti s katerega koli strežnika v "
"omrežju. </para></listitem> <listitem><para> <userinput>&plus;</userinput> – "
"Kanali, ki ne podpirajo kanalskih načinov. To pomeni, da so vsi načini "
"nenastavljeni, razen zastavice kanala 't', ki je nastavljena. </para></"
"listitem> </itemizedlist> Imena kanalov so dolga do 50 znakov in lahko "
"vsebujejo poljubne znake razen presledka, vejice in Ctrl-G (^G ali ASCII 7)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Connect"
msgstr "Hitra povezava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you want to connect to a server without going through the trouble "
"of creating a new server in the <link linkend=\"serverlist\">Server List</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se želite povezati s strežnikom, ne da bi imeli težave z ustvarjanjem "
"novega strežnika na <link linkend=\"serverlist\">Seznamu strežnikov</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>File</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Quick Connect</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The <guilabel>Quick "
"Connect</guilabel> screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"V glavnem meniju izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Datoteka</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Hitra povezava</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. <action>Pojavil se bo "
"zaslon <guilabel>Hitra povezava</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Quick Connect screen."
msgstr "Zaslon za hitro povezavo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Quick Connect screen"
msgstr "Zaslon za hitro povezavo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the server address in the <guilabel>Server host</guilabel> box, your "
"desired &i18n-nickname; in the <guilabel>Nick</guilabel> box, and click the "
"<guibutton>Connect</guibutton> button. When &konversation; has connected to "
"the server, enter command <userinput><command>/join</command> "
"<replaceable>#channelname</replaceable></userinput> to join a channel."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite naslov strežnika v polje <guilabel>Gostitelj strežnika</guilabel>, "
"vaš želeni  &i18n-nickname; v polju <guilabel>Nick</guilabel> in kliknite "
"gumb <guibutton>Poveži</guibutton>. Ko se je &konversation; povezal s "
"strežnikom, vnesite ukaz <userinput><command>/join</command> "
"<replaceable>#channelname</replaceable></userinput>, da se pridružite kanalu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently-used &irc; commands"
msgstr "Pogosto uporabljeni &irc; ukazi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following is a short list of frequently-used &irc; commands. See <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc2812.html\">RFC 2812</ulink> for a "
"complete list of all commands, or visit <ulink url=\"https://www.irchelp.org/"
"\">irchelp.org</ulink>. For a list of commands treated specially by "
"&konversation;, see <link linkend=\"konvi-cmds\">&konversation; commands</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Sledi kratek seznam pogosto uporabljenih &irc; ukazov. Glejte <ulink url="
"\"http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/rfc2812.html\">RFC 2812</ulink> za popoln seznam "
"vseh ukazov ali obiščite <ulink url=\"https://www. irchelp.org/\">irchelp."
"org</ulink>. Za seznam ukazov, ki jih &konversation; posebej obravnava, "
"glejte <link linkend=\"konvi-cmds\">&konversation; ukazi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lists commands available on the current server. Not supported by all servers."
msgstr ""
"Navede ukaze, ki so na voljo na trenutnem strežniku. Ne podpirajo ga vsi "
"strežniki."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/help </command><replaceable>cmd</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/help </command><replaceable>cmd</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides help for <userinput><replaceable>cmd</replaceable></userinput>. Not "
"supported by all servers."
msgstr ""
"Nudi pomoč za <userinput><replaceable>cmd</replaceable></userinput>. Ne "
"podpirajo vsi strežniki."

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid "/join <replaceable>#channel</replaceable>"
msgstr "/join <replaceable>#channel</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins <userinput><replaceable>#channel</replaceable></userinput>. If the "
"channel does not already exist, it is created and you are the channel "
"operator."
msgstr ""
"Pridruži se <userinput><replaceable>#channel</replaceable></userinput>. Če "
"kanal še ne obstaja, je ustvarjen in vi ste operater kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Leaves the current channel and closes the <interface>channel</interface> tab."
msgstr "Zapusti trenutni kanal in zapre zavihek <interface>kanal</interface>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/part </command> <replaceable>#channel</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/part </command> <replaceable>#channel</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Leaves <userinput><replaceable>#channel</replaceable></userinput> and closes "
"the corresponding <interface>channel</interface> tab. Synonym for "
"<userinput><command>/leave</command></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Zapusti <userinput><replaceable>#channel</replaceable></userinput> in zapre "
"ustrezen zavihek <interface>channel</interface>. Sinonim za "
"<userinput><command>/leave</command></userinput>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/me </command><replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/me </command><replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1173 index.docbook:2251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> to the channel "
"preceded by your &i18n-nickname;. For example, if your &i18n-nickname; were "
"<userinput><replaceable>Tux</replaceable></userinput>, typing "
"<userinput><replaceable>/me brews a cup of tea.</replaceable></userinput> "
"displays the message <interface>Tux brews a cup of tea.</interface> Unless "
"they've filtered against these types of messages, all users see it. This "
"kind of message is typically used to convey non-verbal information, such as "
"your current emotional state, or what you are physically doing. If you are "
"leaving your workstation for a short time, use the <userinput><command>/"
"away</command></userinput> command instead."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> v kanalu, pred "
"katerim je vaš &i18n-nickname;. Na primer, če je vaš &i18n-nickname; bil "
"<userinput><replaceable>Tux</replaceable></userinput>, tipkanje "
"<userinput><replaceable>/me kuha skodelico čaja.</replaceable></userinput> "
"prikaže sporočilo <interface>Tux kuha skodelico čaja.</interface> Razen če "
"so filtrirali te vrste sporočil, ga vidijo vsi uporabniki. Tovrstno "
"sporočilo se običajno uporablja za posredovanje neverbalnih informacij, kot "
"je vaše trenutno čustveno stanje ali kaj fizično počnete. Če za kratek čas "
"zapustite delovno postajo, namesto tega uporabite ukaz <userinput><command>/"
"away</command></userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/away </command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/away </command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If anyone tries to send you a private message or invite you to a channel, "
"they will be told that you are away from your workstation with "
"<userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Če vam bo kdorkoli poskušal poslati zasebno sporočilo ali vas povabiti na "
"kanal, bo z <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> obveščen, "
"da ste odsotni od svoje delovne postaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cancels an <userinput><command>/away </command> <replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable></userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"Prekliče ukaz <userinput><command>/away </command> <replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1189 index.docbook:2301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/query </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/query </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new tab with the user's <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> for private conversation, commonly known on &irc; "
"as a <link linkend=\"query\">Query</link>. Everything written here is only "
"visible to you and your query partner."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov zavihek z uporabnikovim <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> za zasebni pogovor, splošno znan na &irc; kot <link "
"linkend=\"query\">poizvedbo</link>. Vse, kar je tukaj napisano, je vidno "
"samo vam in vašemu partnerju za poizvedbo."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/msg </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable> <replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/msg </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable> <replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> to the user with "
"&i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput>. Only "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> sees the message. Use "
"<userinput><command>/query</command></userinput> for longer conversations."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> uporabniku z "
"&i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput>. Samo "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> vidi sporočilo. "
"Uporabite <userinput><command>/query</command></userinput> za daljše "
"pogovore."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/invite </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/invite </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invites the user with &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> to join a channel. This command is especially "
"useful if the channel is invite-only."
msgstr ""
"Povabi uporabnika z &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput>, da se pridružite kanalu. Ta ukaz je še posebej "
"uporaben, če je kanal na voljo samo za povabila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Private conversations (queries)"
msgstr "Zasebni pogovori (vprašanja)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A private conversation is one that only you and one other person can see. "
"Private conversations are called \"queries\" in &konversation;. To initiate "
"a private conversation, type <userinput><command>/query </"
"command><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> in any input line, where "
"<replaceable>nick</replaceable> is the &i18n-nickname; of the person you "
"want to talk with. You can also click with the &RMB; on the person's &i18n-"
"nickname; in the <interface>Nick Panel</interface> and choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Open Query</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. <action>A new tab will be "
"created.</action> Announce yourself by sending a message."
msgstr ""
"Zasebni pogovor je tisti, ki ga lahko vidite samo vi in še ena oseba. "
"Zasebni pogovori se v &konversation; imenujejo \"poizvedbe\". Če želite "
"začeti zasebni pogovor, vnesite <userinput><command>/query </"
"command><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> v katero koli vnosno "
"vrstico, kjer je <replaceable>nick</replaceable>  &i18n-nickname; osebe, s "
"katero želite govoriti. Lahko tudi kliknete z &RMB; na  &i18n-nickname; "
"osebe; v <interface>Plošči vzdevkov</interface> in izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Odpri poizvedbo</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. <action>Ustvarjen bo "
"nov zavihek.</action> Oglasite se tako, da pošljete sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Queries are just like channels, except that only you and the other person "
"can participate in the channel."
msgstr ""
"Poizvedbe so podobne kanalom, le da lahko v kanalu sodelujete samo vi in "
"druga oseba."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To leave the query, just close the tab. Note however, that if the other "
"person sends you another message in the query, the tab will open again."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zapustiti poizvedbo, preprosto zaprite zavihek. Upoštevajte pa, da "
"se bo zavihek znova odprl, če vam druga oseba pošlje drugo sporočilo v "
"poizvedbi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To leave all queries, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Close All Open Queries</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main "
"menu, or press <keycap>F11</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zapustiti vse poizvedbe, izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Okno</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Zapri vse odprte poizvedbe</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> v glavnem meniju ali pritisnite tipko <keycap>F11</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When someone else initiates a query with you, &konversation; creates a new "
"tab with their &i18n-nickname;. If you don't wish to talk with the person, "
"close the tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko nekdo drug začne poizvedbo z vami, &konversation; ustvari nov zavihek s "
"svojim  &i18n-nickname; Če ne želite govoriti z osebo, zaprite zavihek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting notifications"
msgstr "Nastavitev obvestil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Notifications</guilabel> are actions that &konversation; will "
"perform whenever an event occurs. Suppose you have &konversation; running, "
"but minimized or hidden behind other application windows on your desktop. If "
"someone wants to communicate with you, or your buddy joins a channel, you'd "
"like to be alerted. Notifications will accomplish this."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Obvestila</guilabel> so dejanja, ki jih &konversation; se bo "
"izvajal vsakič, ko se zgodi dogodek. Recimo, da imate &konversation; deluje, "
"vendar je strnjen ali skrit za okni drugih aplikacij na namizju. Če nekdo "
"želi komunicirati z vami ali se vaš prijatelj pridruži kanalu, bi želeli "
"biti opozorjeni. Obvestila bodo to dosegla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure notifications, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Notifications</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> "
"on the main menu. <action>The <guilabel>Notification Settings</guilabel> "
"screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati obvestila, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj obvestila</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Pojavil se bo zaslon "
"<guilabel>Nastavitve obvestil</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Notification Settings screen."
msgstr "Zaslon z nastavitvami obvestil."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Notification Settings screen"
msgstr "Zaslon z nastavitvami obvestil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to select an event."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, da izberete dogodek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the types of notifications you'd like to happen when the event occurs. "
"(<guilabel>Mark taskbar entry</guilabel> causes the entry in the taskbar to "
"flash when the event occurs.)"
msgstr ""
"Označite vrste obvestil, ki jih želite prejeti ob dogodku. (<guilabel>Označi "
"vnos v opravilni vrstici</guilabel> povzroči, da vnos v opravilni vrstici "
"utripa, ko pride do dogodka.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repeat by selecting another event and checking the notifications desired. "
"When you've configured all the desired notifications, click the "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ponovite tako, da izberete drug dogodek in označite želena obvestila. Ko "
"nastavite vsa želena obvestila, kliknite gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you've set up your notifications, you can enable or disable all "
"notifications using <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Enable Notifications</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Ko nastavite obvestila, lahko omogočite ali onemogočite vsa obvestila z "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Okno</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Omogoči obvestila</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also alert yourself when someone mentions your &i18n-nickname; in a "
"message using &konversation;'s <link linkend=\"highlighting\">highlighting "
"feature</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako se lahko opozorite, ko nekdo omeni vaš &i18n-nickname; v sporočilu "
"z &konversation; <link linkend=\"highlighting\">funkcijo označevanja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monitoring who is online"
msgstr "Spremljanje, kdo je na spletu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; will keep you informed when your buddies are connected to the "
"&irc; network or not."
msgstr ""
"&konversation; vas bo obveščal, ko bodo vaši prijatelji povezani z &irc; "
"omrežjem ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &irc; network is recorded because &i18n-nickname;s are unique across a "
"single &irc; network. The &i18n-nickname; in two different &irc; networks is "
"not necessarily the same person, but the same &i18n-nickname; on two "
"different servers within the same &irc; network generally is the same person."
msgstr ""
"&irc; omrežje je zabeleženo, ker so  &i18n-nickname; edinstveni v enem &irc; "
"omrežju. &i18n-nickname; v dveh različnih &irc; omrežij ni nujno ista oseba, "
"ampak isti &i18n-nickname; na dveh različnih strežnikih znotraj istega &irc; "
"omrežje pa je na splošno ista oseba."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is why it is important to use the same <guilabel>Network</guilabel> for "
"all servers in the same &irc; network, when <link linkend=\"serverlist\"> "
"defining networks, servers, and auto join channels</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zato je pomembno, da uporabite isto <guilabel>Omrežje</guilabel> za vse "
"strežnike v istem &irc; omrežja, ko <link linkend=\"serverlist\"> definirate "
"omrežja, strežnike in kanale za samodejno pridružitev</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate the &i18n-nickname; watching feature, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Watched Nicks</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel> "
"screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati  &i18n-nickname; funkcijo gledanja izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Okno</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Ogledani vzdevki</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Pojavil se bo zaslon "
"<guilabel>Ogledani vzdevki</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Watched Nicks."
msgstr "Opazovani vzdevki."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Watched Nicks"
msgstr "Opazovani vzdevki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &i18n-nickname;s in your watch list are listed here. They are listed "
"under their associated &irc; network. If no &i18n-nickname;s are listed, "
"either you haven't specified any &i18n-nickname;s to watch, or you need to "
"activate the &i18n-nickname; watching feature (see below). Expand each "
"online &i18n-nickname; to see a list of channels the &i18n-nickname; has "
"joined. The icons next to each channel are the same as the icons that appear "
"in the <interface>Nick Panel</interface> in the <link linkend=\"channel-"
"screen-tour\">channel</link> screens."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-nickname; na vašem seznamu opazovanja so navedeni tukaj. Navedeni so "
"pod povezanimi &irc; omrežji. Če na seznamu ni nobenega &i18n-nickname;, "
"niste določili nobenega &i18n-nickname; za ogled ali pa morate aktivirati "
"&i18n-nickname; funkcijo gledanja (glejte spodaj). Razširite vsak spletni "
"&i18n-nickname; za ogled seznama kanalov &i18n-nickname; se je pridružil. "
"Ikone poleg vsakega kanala so enake ikonam, ki se prikažejo v "
"<interface>Plošči vzdevkov</interface> na zaslonih <link linkend=\"channel-"
"screen-tour\">kanala</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The information known about the &i18n-nickname; is displayed here. When the "
"<guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel> screen is first displayed, this "
"information is sparse. Every 20 seconds, one <userinput><command>WHOIS</"
"command></userinput> command is automatically sent to the server to request "
"information for &i18n-nickname;s that do not have any information. This "
"continues until all &i18n-nickname;s have information."
msgstr ""
"Znani podatki o  &i18n-nickname; je prikazano tukaj. Ko je zaslon "
"<guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel> prvič prikazan, so te informacije "
"redke. Vsakih 20 sekund se en ukaz <userinput><command>WHOIS</command></"
"userinput> samodejno pošlje strežniku, da zahteva informacije za  &i18n-"
"nickname;, ki nimajo nobenih informacij. To se nadaljuje, dokler vsi vzdevki "
"nimajo informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a single &i18n-nickname; to watch, open the context menu in the "
"<guilabel>Nick List</guilabel> by clicking with the &RMB; on a &i18n-"
"nickname; and select <guilabel>Add to Watched Nicks</guilabel>. If you want "
"to add several &i18n-nickname;s choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> "
"from the main menu, expand <guilabel>Notifications</guilabel> and click on "
"<guilabel>Watched Nicknames</guilabel>. The <guilabel>Watched Nicknames</"
"guilabel> screen appears."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati en  &i18n-nickname; za ogled odprite kontekstni meni v "
"<guilabel>Seznamu vzdevkov</guilabel> tako, da kliknete z &RMB; na  &i18n-"
"nickname; in izberite <guilabel>Dodaj med opazovane vzdevke</guilabel>. Če "
"želite dodati več  &i18n-nickname; izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju, razširite <guilabel>Obvestila</"
"guilabel> in kliknite na <guilabel>Ogledani vzdevki</guilabel>. Prikaže se "
"zaslon <guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Watched Nicknames</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Opazovani vzdevki</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Watched Nicknames</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Opazovani vzdevki</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box to activate the &i18n-nickname; watcher feature."
msgstr "Označite to polje, da aktivirate &i18n-nickname; funkcijo opazovalca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want the <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel> screen to automatically "
"display when you open &konversation;, check this box."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se zaslon <guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel> samodejno "
"prikaže, ko odprete &konversation;, potrdite to polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel> screen, you may double click on "
"any &i18n-nickname; and this command will be sent to the server. "
"<userinput><command>%u</command></userinput> will be replaced with the &i18n-"
"nickname;. The <userinput><command>%n</command></userinput> is required at "
"the end of the command."
msgstr ""
"Na zaslonu <guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel> lahko dvokliknete poljuben "
"&i18n-nickname; in ta ukaz bo poslan strežniku. <userinput><command>%u</"
"command></userinput> bo nadomeščen z &i18n-nickname;. <userinput><command>"
"%n</command></userinput> je obvezen na koncu ukaza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel> feature works by periodically polling "
"the server. This box sets how often that occurs. Avoid numbers less than 20 "
"seconds because it places excessive load on the server."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija <guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel> deluje tako, da občasno "
"vpraša strežnik. To polje določa, kako pogosto se to zgodi. Izogibajte se "
"številkam, krajšim od 20 sekund, ker pretirano obremenijo strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button when you have finished adding or "
"removing &i18n-nickname;s."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, ko končate z dodajanjem ali "
"odstranjevanjem vzdevkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Note: </emphasis>Whenever you display the <guilabel>Watched Nicks</"
"guilabel> screen, it may take a while before any &i18n-nickname;s are "
"displayed until &konversation; has polled the server. Normally, you leave "
"the <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel> screen running."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Opomba: </emphasis>Kadar koli prikažete zaslon <guilabel>Opazovani "
"vzdevki</guilabel>, lahko traja nekaj časa, preden se prikažejo vsi &i18n-"
"nickname;-i, dokler ni &konversation;  vprašal strežnik. Običajno pustite "
"zaslon <guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel> odprt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; also displays a message in all the <link linkend=\"channel-"
"screen-tour\">channels</link> whenever a user in your <guilabel>Watched "
"Nicknames</guilabel> list connects or disconnects from the server. The "
"message looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"&konversation; prav tako prikaže sporočilo v vseh <link linkend=\"channel-"
"screen-tour\">kanalih</link> vsakič, ko se uporabnik na vašem seznamu "
"<guilabel>Opazovanih vzdevkov</guilabel> poveže ali prekine povezavo s "
"strežnikom. Sporočilo je videti takole:"

#. Tag: computeroutput
#: index.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid "[17:52] [Notify] psn is online (irc.kde.org)."
msgstr "[17:52] [Obvesti] psn je na spletu (irc.kde.org)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1455
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message highlighting"
msgstr "Označevanje sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control how messages are displayed in channel and query screens."
msgstr ""
"Nadzirate lahko, kako so sporočila prikazana na zaslonih kanalov in poizvedb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate the highlighting feature, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure &konversation;</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The <guilabel>Configure</"
"guilabel> screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati zmožnost označevanja, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj &konversation;</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Pojavil se bo zaslon "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Highlighting screen."
msgstr "Zaslon za označevanje."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1489
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Highlighting screen"
msgstr "Zaslon za označevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to select the <guilabel>Highlight</guilabel> screen."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, da izberete zaslon <guilabel>Označi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to add a new item to the <guilabel>Highlight list</guilabel>. "
"When an item in the list is selected, you may edit it in the panel below."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, če želite dodati nov element na <guilabel>Seznam poudarkov</"
"guilabel>. Ko je izbran element na seznamu, ga lahko uredite na spodnji "
"plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a string pattern here. Any message received that matches this pattern, "
"anywhere in the message, will activate the highlighting for the message."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite vzorec niza. Vsako prejeto sporočilo, ki se ujema s tem "
"vzorcem, kjer koli v sporočilu, bo aktiviralo označevanje sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the pattern is found in a message, the entire message will be displayed "
"in the color you select here."
msgstr ""
"Če je vzorec najden v sporočilu, bo celotno sporočilo prikazano v barvi, ki "
"jo izberete tukaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish, &konversation; will play a sound when the pattern is matched. "
"Click the button to choose an audio file to be played. Click the test button "
"to hear the sound."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, &konversation; predvaja zvok, ko se vzorec ujema. Kliknite gumb, "
"da izberete zvočno datoteko, ki jo želite predvajati. Kliknite gumb za "
"testiranje, da slišite zvok."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you'd like for &konversation; to automatically send a reply message when "
"the pattern is matched, enter the message here. Use this feature with "
"caution, as you may annoy &irc; users with too much chatter if not careful. "
"You can also enter &irc; or &konversation; commands here."
msgstr ""
"Če želite za &konversation; za samodejno pošiljanje odgovora, ko se vzorec "
"ujema, vnesite sporočilo tukaj. To funkcijo uporabljajte previdno, saj lahko "
"motite &irc; uporabniki s preveč klepetanjem, če niso previdni. Vnesete "
"lahko tudi &irc; ali &konversation; ukazi tukaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have configured sounds for any of your highlights, you can disable "
"all of them by unchecking this box."
msgstr ""
"Če ste konfigurirali zvoke za katerega koli od svojih poudarkov, jih lahko "
"vse onemogočite tako, da počistite to polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This highlight will only be searched for in chat windows listed here by "
"name, or in all chat windows if the field is left empty. Multiple names have "
"to be separated by commas."
msgstr ""
"Ta poudarek se bo iskal samo v oknih za klepet, ki so tukaj navedena po "
"imenu, ali v vseh oknih za klepet, če je polje prazno. Več imen je treba "
"ločiti z vejicami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this box, whenever someone mentions your &i18n-nickname; in a "
"message, the message will be displayed in the color you choose at the right."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to polje, vsakič, ko nekdo omeni vaš &i18n-nickname; v sporočilu "
"bo sporočilo prikazano v barvi, ki jo izberete na desni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Normally, highlighting does not apply to messages you type. If you wish to "
"highlight the messages you type, check this box and choose a color at the "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Običajno označevanje ne velja za sporočila, ki jih vnesete. Če želite "
"označiti sporočila, ki jih vnesete, potrdite to polje in izberite barvo na "
"desni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring On Screen Display (&osd;)"
msgstr "Konfiguracija prikaza na zaslonu (&osd;)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>On Screen Display</acronym> (&osd;) is a unique feature of "
"&konversation;. With &osd; turned on, channel messages will appear on your "
"desktop screen, even if &konversation; is minimized. Here's an example of "
"&osd; in action. The message in the upper lefthand part of the screen is "
"from &konversation;, which is running minimized in the system tray."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>Zaslonski prikaz</acronym> (&osd;) je edinstvena funkcija "
"&konversation;. Z &osd; vklopljeno, bodo sporočila kanala prikazana na "
"namizju, tudi če je &konversation; strnjen. Tukaj je primer &osd; v akciji. "
"Sporočilo v zgornjem levem delu zaslona je iz &konversation;, ki se izvaja "
"pomanjšano v sistemskem pladnju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1551
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Example of On Screen Display</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primer prikaza na zaslonu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1557
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Example of On Screen Display</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primer prikaza na zaslonu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate &osd;, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Configure &konversation;</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main "
"menu. <action>The <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati &osd;, izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj &konversation;</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Pojavil se bo zaslon "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1573
#, no-c-format
msgid "The On Screen Display screen."
msgstr "Zaslon na zaslonu."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1589
#, no-c-format
msgid "The On Screen Display screen"
msgstr "Zaslon na zaslonu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to expand the <guilabel>Notification</guilabel> item."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, da razširite element <guilabel>Obvestilo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to select the <guilabel>On Screen Display</guilabel> screen."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da izberete zaslon <guilabel>Zaslonski prikaz</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1602
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box to activate &osd;."
msgstr "Označite to polje, da aktivirate &osd;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to choose a font for &osd;. (<emphasis>Note: </emphasis> "
"Not all fonts work. Luxi Sans 22 and Impact 22 are known to work.)"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, da izberete pisavo za &osd;. (<emphasis>Opomba: </"
"emphasis> Vse pisave ne delujejo. Znano je, da delujeta Luxi Sans 22 in "
"Impact 22.)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the boxes here to select the types of messages you'd like to appear on "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj potrdite polja, da izberete vrste sporočil, ki jih želite prikazati na "
"zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Drag the <interface>&osd; Preview</interface> to your desired position, then "
"click the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Povlecite <interface>&osd; Predogled</interface> na želeni položaj, nato "
"kliknite gumb <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending colorful messages"
msgstr "Pošiljanje barvitih sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add color to the messages you send in any channel. In the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface> of any channel, start typing your message. "
"Click the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"color.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Insert "
"&irc; Color Button</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guibutton>&irc; Color</guibutton> button or choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Insert</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>&irc; Color</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The <guilabel>&irc; Color Chooser</"
"guilabel> screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Sporočilom, ki jih pošljete v katerem koli kanalu, lahko dodate barvo. V "
"<interface>Vnosna vrstica</interface> katerega koli kanala začnite vnašati "
"svoje sporočilo. Kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"format-text-color.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> "
"<textobject> <phrase>Insert &irc; Gumb barva</phrase> </textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>&irc; Barva</guibutton> gumb ali izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Vstavi</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>&irc; Barva</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action><guilabel>&irc; Prikaže "
"se zaslon za izbiro barve</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1640
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &irc; Color Chooser screen."
msgstr "&irc; zaslon za izbiro barv."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1646
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &irc; Color Chooser screen"
msgstr "&irc; zaslon za izbiro barv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a color and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. Continue typing your "
"message in the <interface>Input Line</interface>. To change the color again, "
"click the <guibutton>&irc; Color</guibutton> button. Choose a different "
"color and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite barvo in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>. Nadaljujte s "
"tipkanjem sporočila v <interface>Vnosna vrstica</interface>. Če želite znova "
"spremeniti barvo, kliknite gumb <guibutton>&irc; Barva</guibutton>. Izberite "
"drugo barvo in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &i18n-nickname; themes"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &i18n-nickname; teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the icons displayed next to &i18n-nickname;s in the "
"<interface>Nick Panel</interface> of channel tabs. To change the &i18n-"
"nickname; theme, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main "
"menu. <action>The <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> screen will appear.</"
"action> Click <guilabel>Interface</guilabel> to expand it, then click "
"<guilabel>Nicklist Themes</guilabel> to display the <guilabel>Nicklist "
"Themes</guilabel> screen."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite lahko ikone, prikazane poleg  &i18n-nickname; v <interface>plošči "
"vzdevkov</interface> zavihkov kanala. Če želite spremeniti vzdevek &i18n-"
"nickname; temo izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem "
"meniju. <action>Pojavil se bo zaslon <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>.</"
"action> Kliknite <guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel>, da ga razširite, nato "
"kliknite <guilabel>Teme seznama nadomestkov</guilabel>, da prikažete "
"<guilabel> Zaslon Teme</guilabel> s seznamom nadomestkov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1679
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Themes screen."
msgstr "Zaslon Teme."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1693
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Themes screen"
msgstr "Zaslon Teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1702
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to select the <guilabel>Nicklist Themes</guilabel> screen."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da izberete zaslon <guilabel>Teme seznama nadomestkov</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a theme."
msgstr "Izberite temo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sample icons are displayed here in the chosen theme."
msgstr "Vzorci ikon so prikazani tukaj v izbrani temi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have downloaded a nick theme from elsewhere, click to install it."
msgstr "Če ste temo vzdevka prenesli od drugod, kliknite, da jo namestite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Quick Buttons"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje hitrih gumbov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enable a feature to display <interface>Quick Buttons</interface> on "
"the <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Main</link> screen, eight "
"<interface>Quick Buttons</interface> appear. To display the Quick Buttons, "
"choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The "
"<guilabel>Configure</guilabel> screen will appear.</action> Click "
"<guilabel>Interface</guilabel> to expand it, then click <guilabel>Chat "
"Window</guilabel>. Check the <guilabel>Show quick buttons</guilabel> box and "
"click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite lahko funkcijo za prikaz <interface>hitrih gumbov</interface> na "
"<link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">glavnem</link> zaslonu, prikaže se "
"osem <interface>hitrih gumbov</interface>. Za prikaz hitrih gumbov izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Pojavil se "
"bo zaslon <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>.</action> Kliknite "
"<guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel>, da ga razširite, nato kliknite <guilabel>Okno "
"za klepet</guilabel>. Označite polje <guilabel>Pokaži hitre gumbe</guilabel> "
"in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The buttons may be customized to your liking for performing often-used &irc; "
"commands. To customize the <interface>Quick Buttons</interface>, choose "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The "
"<guilabel>Configure</guilabel> screen will appear.</action> Click "
"<guilabel>Interface</guilabel> to expand it, then click <guilabel>Quick "
"Buttons</guilabel> to display the <guilabel>Quick Buttons</guilabel> screen."
msgstr ""
"Gumbe lahko prilagodite svojim željam za izvajanje pogosto uporabljenih "
"&irc; ukazi. Če želite prilagoditi <interface>Hitre gumbe</interface>, "
"izberite <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem "
"meniju. <action>Pojavil se bo zaslon <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>.</"
"action> Kliknite <guilabel>Vmesnik</guilabel>, da ga razširite, nato "
"kliknite <guilabel>Hitre gumbe</guilabel>, da prikažete <guilabel> Zaslon s "
"hitrimi gumbi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Quick Buttons screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zaslon hitrih gumbov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1748
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Quick Buttons screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zaslon s hitrimi gumbi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are 8 default <interface>Quick Button</interface>s. Click on an entry "
"to change it or use the buttons at the right side of the list to add or "
"remove <interface>Quick Button</interface>s. The <guilabel>Button Name</"
"guilabel> column is the name that will appear on the button in the <link "
"linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Main</link> screen. Keep the names short. "
"The <guilabel>Button Action</guilabel> column is the action that will be "
"performed when you click the <interface>Quick Button</interface>. Tips for "
"creating actions are given on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja 8 privzetih <interface>hitrih gumbov</interface>. Kliknite na vnos, "
"da ga spremenite, ali uporabite gumbe na desni strani seznama, da dodate ali "
"odstranite <interface>Hitre gumbe</interface>. Stolpec <guilabel>Ime gumba</"
"guilabel> je ime, ki bo prikazano na gumbu na <link linkend=\"channel-screen-"
"tour\">glavnem</link> zaslonu. Imena naj bodo kratka. Stolpec "
"<guilabel>Dejanje gumba</guilabel> je dejanje, ki bo izvedeno, ko kliknete "
"<interface>Hitri gumb</interface>. Nasveti za ustvarjanje dejanj so "
"prikazani na zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1763
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to complete the changes."
msgstr "Kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da dokončate spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Primer:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Button Name</guilabel>: <userinput><replaceable>Msg</replaceable></"
"userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime gumba</guilabel>: <userinput><replaceable>Sporočilo</"
"replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Button Action</guilabel>: <userinput><replaceable>Msg %u </"
"replaceable></userinput> (there is a space after <userinput><replaceable>%u</"
"replaceable></userinput>)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dejanje gumba</guilabel>: <userinput><replaceable>Sporočilo %u </"
"replaceable></userinput> (za <userinput><replaceable>%u</replaceable></"
"userinput> je presledek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use this button in the <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Main</link> "
"screen, click on a &i18n-nickname; in the <interface>Nick Panel</interface>, "
"then click the button. <computeroutput>/MSG </computeroutput> will appear in "
"the <interface>Input Line</interface> followed by the chosen &i18n-"
"nickname;. Type a message you want to send to that person and press &Enter;. "
"The message will be sent to the user. Only that user will see the message."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo tega gumba na <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">glavnem</"
"link> zaslonu kliknite &i18n-nickname; v <interface>plošči vzdevkov</"
"interface>, nato kliknite gumb. <computeroutput>/MSG </computeroutput> se "
"prikaže v <interface>Vnosni vrstici</interface>, ki mu sledi izbrani &i18n-"
"nickname;. Vnesite sporočilo, ki ga želite poslati tej osebi, in pritisnite "
"&Enter;. Sporočilo bo poslano uporabniku. Samo ta uporabnik bo videl "
"sporočilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending and receiving files"
msgstr "Pošiljanje in prejemanje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may send files via &irc; to other users online, or they may send you "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke lahko pošiljate prek &irc; drugim uporabnikom na spletu ali vam "
"lahko pošljejo datoteke."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"WARNING: Never open a file someone sends you unless they are a trusted "
"source. It could be a virus."
msgstr ""
"OPOZORILO: Nikoli ne odpirajte datoteke, ki vam jo nekdo pošlje, razen če je "
"zaupanja vreden vir. Lahko je virus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To send a file to someone in a channel, click with the &RMB; on the &i18n-"
"nickname; of the person in the <interface>Nick Panel</interface> of the "
"<link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Main</link> screen. Choose "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Send File</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> <action>. A "
"dialog appears for you to choose a file to send.</action> Next, a new "
"<guilabel>DCC Status</guilabel> tab appears."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poslati datoteko nekomu v kanalu, kliknite z &RMB; na &i18n-"
"nickname; osebe v <interface>Plošči  vzdevkov</interface> na <link linkend="
"\"channel-screen-tour\">glavnem</link> zaslonu. Izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Pošlji datoteko</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> <action>. Prikaže se "
"pogovorno okno, v katerem izberete datoteko za pošiljanje.</action> Nato se "
"prikaže nov zavihek <guilabel>Status DCC</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1819
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>DCC Status tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zavihek Stanje DCC</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1832
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>DCC Status tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihek Stanje DCC</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &i18n-nickname; of the recipient and file name appear here."
msgstr "&i18n-nickname; prejemnika in ime datoteke sta prikazana tukaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Status</guilabel> column indicates the status of the file send "
"or receive as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Stolpec <guilabel>Stanje</guilabel> označuje status poslane ali prejete "
"datoteke, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1850
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preparing"
msgstr "Priprava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A receiving transfer is checking for resumable files or a sending transfer "
"is acquiring the data to send."
msgstr ""
"Prejemni prenos preverja datoteke, ki jih je mogoče nadaljevati, ali "
"pošiljajoči prenos pridobiva podatke za pošiljanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1860
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connecting"
msgstr "Povezovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1863
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; is trying to establish a connection with the other end."
msgstr "&konversation; poskuša vzpostaviti povezavo z drugim koncem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sending"
msgstr "Pošiljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1872
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; is sending the file to the other end."
msgstr "&konversation; pošilja datoteko na drugo stran."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Receiving"
msgstr "Prejemanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1881
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; is receiving the file from the other end."
msgstr "&konversation; prejema datoteko z drugega konca."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Končano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1890
#, no-c-format
msgid "The file has been successfully transferred."
msgstr "Datoteka je bila uspešno prenesena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pending"
msgstr "V teku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1899
#, no-c-format
msgid "The transfer is waiting for the partner to accept or reject it."
msgstr "Nakazilo čaka, da ga partner sprejme ali zavrne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aborted"
msgstr "Prekinjeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Either you clicked the <guibutton>Abort</guibutton> button, or the other "
"person aborted the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ali ste kliknili gumb <guibutton>Prekini</guibutton> ali pa je druga oseba "
"prekinila prenos."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Failed"
msgstr "Ni uspelo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid "An error occurred and the transfer was not successful."
msgstr "Prišlo je do napake in prenos ni bil uspešen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1923
#, no-c-format
msgid "Queued"
msgstr "V čakalni vrsti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfer is waiting for you to accept or reject it."
msgstr "Prenos čaka, da ga sprejmete ali zavrnete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1941
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resuming"
msgstr "Nadaljevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a transfer begins but the file already exists on the user's system, the "
"user will be prompted <interface>File already exists. Resume transfer?</"
"interface> This status indicates the user resumed the transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ko se prenos začne, vendar datoteka že obstaja v uporabnikovem sistemu, bo "
"uporabnik pozvan <interface>Datoteka že obstaja. Želite nadaljevati prenos?</"
"interface> To stanje pomeni, da je uporabnik nadaljeval prenos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When someone wants to send you a file, the <guilabel>DCC Status</guilabel> "
"tab will be created (if not already created). Click the <guilabel>DCC "
"Status</guilabel> tab to display it. Click the file to select it, then click "
"this button to accept the file and the transfer will begin. <emphasis>Note: "
"</emphasis>You may configure &konversation; to automatically accept sends "
"from other people by choosing <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main "
"menu. Click <guilabel>Behavior</guilabel> to expand it, then click "
"<guilabel>DCC</guilabel> to display the <guilabel>DCC</guilabel> screen."
msgstr ""
"Ko vam nekdo želi poslati datoteko, bo ustvarjen zavihek <guilabel>Status "
"DCC</guilabel> (če še ni ustvarjen). Kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Status DCC</"
"guilabel>, da ga prikažete. Kliknite datoteko, da jo izberete, nato kliknite "
"ta gumb, da sprejmete datoteko in prenos se bo začel. <emphasis>Opomba: </"
"emphasis>Lahko konfigurirate &konversation; za samodejno sprejemanje "
"pošiljanj od drugih oseb z izbiro <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> "
"v glavnem meniju. Kliknite <guilabel>Vedenje</guilabel>, da ga razširite, "
"nato kliknite <guilabel>DCC</guilabel>, da prikažete zaslon <guilabel>DCC</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have trouble sending or receiving files, your firewall or router may "
"be blocking DCC ports. See <link linkend=\"faq\">Questions and Answers</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate težave pri pošiljanju ali prejemanju datotek, vaš požarni zid ali "
"usmerjevalnik morda blokira vrata DCC. Glejte <link linkend=\"faq"
"\">Vprašanja in odgovori</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1977
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capturing &URL;s from messages"
msgstr "Zajemanje &URL; iz sporočil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In any <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">channel</link>, users sometimes "
"post the &URL;s of interesting websites or other resources on the web. You "
"can double-click any such &URL; and &konversation; will launch the "
"application associated with the &URL;. The application launched depends upon "
"the &MIME; type of the &URL;. For example, a &URL; beginning with "
"<interface>https:</interface> will activate your default web browser and "
"display the web page. (You can also specify the <link linkend=\"webbrowser"
"\">web browser</link> to use.) If the &URL; scrolls off the screen, you "
"might have trouble finding it again. &konversation; can keep a convenient "
"list of all &URL;s for you. To activate this feature, choose <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>&URL; Catcher</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>A new tab called <guilabel>&URL; "
"Catcher</guilabel> is created.</action>"
msgstr ""
"V katerem koli <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">kanalu</link> "
"uporabniki včasih objavijo &URL;-je zanimivih spletnih mest ali drugih virov "
"v spletu. Vsak tak &URL; lahko dvakrat kliknete. in &konversation; bo zagnal "
"aplikacijo, povezano z &URL;. Zagnana aplikacija je odvisna od &MIME; vrsto "
"&URL;. Na primer &URL; ki se začne z <interface>http:</interface>, bo "
"aktiviral vaš privzeti spletni brskalnik in prikazal spletno stran. "
"(Določite lahko tudi <link linkend=\"webbrowser\">spletni brskalnik</link> "
"za uporabo.) Če &URL; pomakne z zaslona, boste morda imeli težave pri "
"ponovnem iskanju. &konversation; lahko vodi priročen seznam vseh &URL;ov za "
"vas. Če želite aktivirati to funkcijo, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Okno</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>&URL; Lovilnik</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Nov zavihek z imenom <guilabel>&URL; "
"Lovilnik</guilabel> je ustvarjen.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1997
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &URL; Catcher tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zavihek &URL; lovilnik.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2013
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &URL; Catcher tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zavihek &URL; lovilnik.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the list of &URL;s seen since you started &konversation;. The "
"<guilabel>From</guilabel> column is the &i18n-nickname; of the person who "
"posted the &URL; or the name of the channel or server, where the &URL; was "
"posted. (&URL;s appearing in join and leave messages are not listed.) Click "
"on a &URL; to select it."
msgstr ""
"To je seznam videnih &URL;, odkar ste začeli &konversation;. Stolpec "
"<guilabel>Od</guilabel> je &i18n-nickname;  osebe, ki je objavila &URL; ali "
"ime kanala ali strežnika, kjer &URL; je bilo objavljeno. (URL-ji, ki se "
"pojavljajo v sporočilih za pridružitev in zapuščanje, niso navedeni.) "
"Kliknite na &URL; da ga izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to activate the application associated with the selected &URL;. "
"The application launched depends upon the &MIME; type of the &URL;. For "
"example, a &URL; beginning with <interface>https:</interface> will activate "
"your default web browser and display the web page. For web pages, you can "
"also specify the <link linkend=\"webbrowser\">web browser</link> to use."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, da aktivirate aplikacijo, povezano z izbranim &URL;. Zagnana "
"aplikacija je odvisna od &MIME; vrste&URL;. Na primer &URL; ki se začne z "
"<interface>http:</interface>, bo aktiviral vaš privzeti spletni brskalnik in "
"prikazal spletno stran. Za spletne strani lahko določite tudi <link linkend="
"\"webbrowser\">spletni brskalnik</link>, ki ga želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to copy the selected &URL; to the clipboard."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, če želite kopirati izbrani &URL; v odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2032
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to delete the selected &URL; from the list."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, če želite izbrisati izbrani &URL; s seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2034
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to save the list of &URL;s to a file."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, če želite seznam &URL;s shraniti v datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to clear the list."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj, da počistite seznam."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting your preferred web browser"
msgstr "Nastavitev želenega spletnega brskalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click on a highlighted &URL; anywhere in &konversation;, it will "
"launch the default application associated with the &MIME; type of the &URL;. "
"For example, when clicking on a &URL; beginning with <interface>https</"
"interface>, &konqueror; is launched to display the web page. You can specify "
"an application different from the <guilabel>Default Applications</guilabel> "
"module of the &systemsettings;. For example, you can use "
"<application>Firefox</application> instead."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete označen &URL; kjer koli v &konversation;, bo zagnal privzeto "
"aplikacijo, povezano z &MIME; vrsto &URL;. Na primer, ko kliknete na &URL; "
"ki se začne z <interface>http</interface>, se zažene &konqueror; za prikaz "
"spletne strani. Določite lahko aplikacijo, ki se razlikuje od modula "
"<guilabel>Privzete aplikacije</guilabel> v &systemsettings;. Namesto tega "
"lahko na primer uporabite <application>Firefox</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose a different web browser from &konversation; app, choose "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"&konversation;</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu. <action>The "
"<guilabel>Configure</guilabel> screen will appear.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati drug spletni brskalnik iz &konversation; izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj "
"&konversation;</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju. <action>Pojavil "
"se bo zaslon <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>.</action>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2065
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The General screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zaslon Splošno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2078
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The General screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zaslon Splošno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2087
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to display the <guilabel>General</guilabel> screen."
msgstr "Kliknite tukaj za prikaz zaslona <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2089
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click here to specify that you want to use a custom web browser."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, če želite določiti, da želite uporabljati spletni brskalnik "
"po meri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the command to launch your desired web browser. When you click on a "
"&URL; <userinput><replaceable>%u</replaceable></userinput> will be replaced "
"with the &URL;."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ukaz za zagon želenega spletnega brskalnika. Ko kliknete na &URL; "
"<userinput><replaceable>%u</replaceable></userinput> bo zamenjan z &URL;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Note: </emphasis>The web browser setting does not apply to "
"<interface>mailto:</interface> &URL;s. <interface>mailto:</interface> &URL;s "
"always launch the default mailer."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Opomba: </emphasis>Nastavitve spletnega brskalnika ne veljajo za "
"<interface>mailto:</interface> &URL;. <interface>mailto:</interface> &URL; "
"vedno zažene privzeti poštni program."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> to save your changes. You must reconnect "
"to each server and channel for the changes to take effect. The easiest way "
"to do this is to quit and restart &konversation;."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>, da shranite spremembe. Za "
"uveljavitev sprememb se morate znova povezati z vsakim strežnikom in "
"kanalom. Najlažji način za to je, da zaprete in znova zaženete "
"&konversation;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Marking Channel and Query Logs"
msgstr "Označevanje dnevnikov kanalov in poizvedb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert a marker into <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">channel</"
"link> and <link linkend=\"query\">query</link> screens to help you quickly "
"locate information. To do this, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Insert</"
"guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Marker Line</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main "
"menu, or press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo>. <action>A line will appear at the bottom of the text on the "
"screen. The line will scroll with the rest of the text on the screen.</"
"action>"
msgstr ""
"V zaslone <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">kanala</link> in <link "
"linkend=\"query\">poizvedbe</link> lahko vstavite oznako, ki vam pomaga "
"hitro najti informacije. To storite tako, da v glavnem meniju izberete "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Vstavi</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Črta označevanja</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> ali pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R </keycap></keycombo>. <action>Na dnu besedila na zaslonu se bo "
"pojavila vrstica. Vrstica se bo premikala skupaj s preostalim besedilom na "
"zaslonu.</action>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make the <interface>Maker Line</interface> be inserted in all channels "
"and queries at once, choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Configure Konversation</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> from the main "
"menu, expand <guilabel>Behavior</guilabel>, click on <guilabel>Chat Window</"
"guilabel>, and check the <guilabel>Show manually inserted lines in all chat "
"windows</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, da se <interface>Črta označevanja</interface> vstavi v vse kanale "
"in poizvedbe hkrati, v glavnem meniju izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Konversation</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> razširite <guilabel>Vedenje</guilabel>, kliknite "
"<guilabel>Okno za klepet</guilabel> in potrdite polje <guilabel>Pokaži ročno "
"vstavljene vrstice v vseh oknih za klepet</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make &konversation; automatically insert a <interface>Marker Line</"
"interface> whenever you do an <userinput><command>/away</command> "
"<replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> command, see <link linkend="
"\"identity-away\">Setting your identity</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite &konversation; samodejno vstavite <interface>Marker Line</"
"interface> vsakič, ko naredite ukaz <userinput><command>/away</command> "
"<replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput>, glejte <link linkend=\"identity-"
"away\">Nastavitev vaše identitete</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "Beleženje dnevnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If logging is enabled, &konversation; keeps a log of each <interface>Server</"
"interface>, <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Channel</link>, and <link "
"linkend=\"query\">Private conversation (query)</link> session. Each session "
"is stored in a log file on disk. When you open the same session again, "
"&konversation; appends to the log."
msgstr ""
"Če je beleženje omogočeno, &konversation; vodi dnevnik vsakega "
"<interface>strežnika</interface>, <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour"
"\">kanala</link> in <link linkend=\"query\">zasebnega pogovora (poizvedbe)</"
"link> sejo. Vsaka seja je shranjena v dnevniški datoteki na disku. Ko "
"ponovno odprete isto sejo, se &konversation; priloži dnevniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever you open a session again, approximately the last 1024 characters of "
"the previous session are read from the tail of the log and shown on the "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli znova odprete sejo, se približno zadnjih 1024 znakov prejšnje seje "
"prebere z repa dnevnika in prikaže na zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As your session continues, messages scroll off the top of the display. You "
"can scroll backwards to view these messages. Eventually, in order to "
"conserve memory, the oldest messages are discarded from the scroll. This is "
"called the <guilabel>Scrollback limit</guilabel>. Messages that disappear "
"from the display because of the <guilabel>Scrollback limit</guilabel> are "
"still available in the log file, if logging is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ko se vaša seja nadaljuje, se sporočila pomaknejo z vrha zaslona. Za ogled "
"teh sporočil se lahko pomaknete nazaj. Sčasoma se najstarejša sporočila "
"zaradi varčevanja s pomnilnikom izločijo iz zvitka. To se imenuje "
"<guilabel>Omejitev drsenja nazaj</guilabel>. Sporočila, ki izginejo iz "
"prikaza zaradi <guilabel>Omejitve pomika nazaj</guilabel>, so še vedno na "
"voljo v dnevniški datoteki, če je beleženje omogočeno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the logfile for a session, click the tab for the session to make it "
"the current session and choose <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Window</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Open Logfile</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> from the main menu. "
"<action>A new tab appears</action> displaying the log file."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati dnevniško datoteko za sejo, kliknite zavihek za sejo, "
"da postane trenutna seja, in v glavnem meniju izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Okno</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Odpri dnevniško datoteko</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> . <action>Prikaže se nov zavihek</action>, ki "
"prikazuje dnevniško datoteko."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Logfile</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dnevniška datoteka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2192
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Logfile</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dnevniška datoteka</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The messages in the log file are displayed here. The oldest messages are at "
"the top and the most recent are at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj so prikazana sporočila v dnevniški datoteki. Najstarejša sporočila so "
"na vrhu, najnovejša pa na dnu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to save the log file to another file."
msgstr "Kliknite ta gumb, da shranite dnevniško datoteko v drugo datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click to refresh the log file display. While you are viewing a log file, "
"newer messages in the corresponding session are <emphasis>not</emphasis> "
"automatically added to the log file display. Use this button to view the "
"most recent messages."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite za osvežitev prikaza dnevniške datoteke. Medtem ko si ogledujete "
"dnevniško datoteko, se novejša sporočila v ustrezni seji <emphasis>ne</"
"emphasis> samodejno dodajo na prikaz dnevniške datoteke. S tem gumbom si "
"lahko ogledate najnovejša sporočila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click to erase the log file display and the log file on disk."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite, da izbrišete prikaz dnevniške datoteke in dnevniško datoteko na "
"disku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this box to set the maximum size of the scroll. This setting does take "
"effect only for newly opened log tabs. The last changed value of the scroll "
"size will be used on &konversation;'s next start. Each log file may have a "
"separate setting."
msgstr ""
"S tem poljem nastavite največjo velikost zvitka. Ta nastavitev velja le za "
"na novo odprte zavihke dnevnika. Zadnja spremenjena vrednost velikosti "
"drsnika bo uporabljena ob naslednjem zagonu &konversation;. Vsaka dnevniška "
"datoteka ima lahko ločeno nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Scrollback limit</guilabel> can be changed by choosing "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"&konversation;</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu, then expand "
"<guilabel>Behavior</guilabel> and click on <guilabel>Chat Window</guilabel>. "
"The <guilabel>Scrollback limit</guilabel> box appears on this screen. If you "
"set it to <guilabel>Unlimited</guilabel> (&ie; zero), messages are not "
"discarded from the scroll."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Omejitev drsenja nazaj</guilabel> lahko spremenite tako, da v "
"glavnem meniju izberete <menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj &konversation;</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> in nato "
"razširite <guilabel> Vedenje</guilabel> in kliknite na <guilabel>Okno za "
"klepet</guilabel>. Na tem zaslonu se prikaže polje <guilabel>Omejitev pomika "
"nazaj</guilabel>. Če ga nastavite na <guilabel>Neomejeno</guilabel> (&ie;. "
"nič), sporočila niso zavržena iz drsenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enable or disable logging and set other logging options, by choosing "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"&konversation;</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu, then expand "
"<guilabel>Behavior</guilabel> and click on <guilabel>Logging</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Beleženje lahko omogočite ali onemogočite in nastavite druge možnosti "
"beleženja tako, da v glavnem meniju izberete <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj &konversation;</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> in nato razširite <guilabel>Vedenje </guilabel> in "
"kliknite na <guilabel>Beleženje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2239
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; commands"
msgstr "&konversation; ukazi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following commands are interpreted by &konversation; and may differ from "
"standard &irc; commands. Items inside square brackets are optional. Items "
"separated by bar (|) are alternate forms of the command. Commands not listed "
"here are sent to the server as entered."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje ukaze razlaga &konversation; in se lahko razlikujejo od "
"standardnih &irc; ukazov. Elementi v oglatih oklepajih niso obvezni. "
"Elementi, ločeni s črto (|), so nadomestne oblike ukaza. Ukazi, ki niso "
"navedeni tukaj, se pošljejo na strežnik, kot so vneseni."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/me</command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/me</command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/ame</command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/ame</command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like the <userinput><command>/me</command></userinput> command above except "
"that the message is sent to all the channels and queries you have open on "
"all the servers you have connected in &konversation;."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot zgornji ukaz <userinput><command>/me</command></userinput>, le da "
"je sporočilo poslano vsem kanalom in poizvedbam, ki ste jih odprli na vseh "
"strežnikih, ki ste jih povezali v &konversation;."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/join</command> <replaceable>channel</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[pwd]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/join</command> <replaceable>kanal</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[pwd]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput>. If the "
"server permits it, and if the channel does not already exist, it is created "
"and you are the channel operator. If the channel requires a password in "
"order to join, specify as <userinput><replaceable>pwd</replaceable></"
"userinput>. Most channel names begin with <userinput><replaceable>#</"
"replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Pridruži se <userinput><replaceable>kanalu</replaceable></userinput>. Če "
"strežnik to dovoli in če kanal še ne obstaja, se ustvari in vi ste operater "
"kanala. Če kanal zahteva geslo za pridružitev, navedite kot "
"<userinput><replaceable>pwd</replaceable></userinput>. Večina imen kanalov "
"se začne z <userinput><replaceable>#</replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/j</command> <replaceable>channel</replaceable> <replaceable>[pwd]</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/j</command> <replaceable>channel</replaceable> <replaceable>[pwd]</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Same as <userinput><command>/join</command></userinput> above."
msgstr "Enako kot <userinput><command>/join</command></userinput> zgoraj."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/part</command> <replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[reason]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/part</command> <replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[reason]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Leaves <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput> with "
"<userinput><replaceable>reason</replaceable></userinput> and closes the "
"corresponding <interface>channel</interface> tab. Within a &konversation; "
"channel or query tab, you can just enter <userinput><command>/part</"
"command></userinput> which closes that channel or query with your default "
"reason as given in the <link linkend=\"identity\">Settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zapusti <userinput><replaceable>kanal</replaceable></userinput> z "
"<userinput><replaceable>razlogom</replaceable></userinput> in zapre ustrezen "
"zavihek <interface>channel</interface>. Znotraj &konversation; zavihek "
"kanala ali poizvedbe, lahko samo vnesete <userinput><command>/part</"
"command></userinput>, ki zapre ta kanal ali poizvedbo z vašim privzetim "
"razlogom, kot je naveden v <link linkend=\"identity\">Nastavitve</link>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/leave</command> <replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[reason]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/leave</command> <replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[reason]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Same as <userinput><command>/part</command></userinput> above."
msgstr "Enako kot <userinput><command>/part</command></userinput> zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When entered in any channel, query, or DCC tab, disconnects from the "
"corresponding server and closes all channel, query, or DCC tabs open on that "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Ko ga vnesete v kateri koli zavihek kanala, poizvedbe ali DCC, prekine "
"povezavo z ustreznim strežnikom in zapre vse zavihke kanala, poizvedbe ali "
"DCC, odprte na tem strežniku."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/notice</command> <replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/notice</command> <replaceable>nick|kanal</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> to the user with "
"&i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> or to "
"everyone in the <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput>. "
"The following is an example of what appears to you in the channel tab"
msgstr ""
"Pošlje <userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> uporabniku z "
"&i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> ali "
"vsem v <userinput><replaceable>kanalu</replaceable></userinput>. Sledi "
"primer tega, kar se vam prikaže na zavihku kanala"

#. Tag: computeroutput
#: index.docbook:2292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[17:14] [Notice] Sending notice \"I think I understand\" to #konversation"
msgstr ""
"[17:14] [Notice] Sending notice \"I think I understand\" to #konversation"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2294
#, no-c-format
msgid "And this is what the recipients see"
msgstr "In to vidijo prejemniki"

#. Tag: computeroutput
#: index.docbook:2296
#, no-c-format
msgid "[17:15] [Notice] -Eisfuchs- I think I understand"
msgstr "[17:15] [Notice] -Eisfuchs- I think I understand"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new tab with the user's <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> for private conversation, commonly known on &irc; "
"as a <link linkend=\"query\">Query</link>. Everything written here is only "
"visible to you and your query partner. You may enter more than one &i18n-"
"nickname; separated by spaces and a query tab will be opened for each &i18n-"
"nickname;. Each such query tab will be private between you and the query "
"partner."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov zavihek z uporabnikovim <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> za zasebni pogovor, splošno znan na &irc; kot <link "
"linkend=\"query\">poizvedbo</link>. Vse, kar je tukaj napisano, je vidno "
"samo vam in vašemu partnerju za poizvedbo. Vnesete lahko več kot en &i18n-"
"nickname; ločeni s presledki in za vsak &i18n-nickname; se bo odprl zavihek "
"s poizvedbo. Vsak tak zavihek za poizvedbo bo zaseben med vami in partnerjem "
"za poizvedbo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>/msg </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable></"
"userinput> <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>/msg </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable></"
"userinput> <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends a private message to the user with &i18n-nickname; "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> or to all users in "
"<userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput>. Unlike "
"<userinput><command>/query</command></userinput>, does not open a new tab. "
"If <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput> begins with "
"<userinput><command>/me </command></userinput>, the message is formatted in "
"the same manner as a <userinput><command>/me</command></userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje zasebno sporočilo uporabniku z &i18n-nickname; "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> ali vsem uporabnikom "
"v <userinput><replaceable>kanalu</replaceable></userinput>. Za razliko od "
"<userinput><command>/query</command></userinput> ne odpre novega zavihka. Če "
"se <userinput><replaceable>sporočilo</replaceable></userinput> začne z "
"<userinput><command>/me </command></userinput>, je sporočilo oblikovano na "
"enak način kot <userinput><command >/me</command></userinput> ukaz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Primeri"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:2314
#, no-c-format
msgid "/msg Eisfuchs I need some help with the msg command"
msgstr "/msg Eisfuchs Potrebujem pomoč pri ukazu msg"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:2316
#, no-c-format
msgid "/msg #konversation New version of Konvi is online!"
msgstr "/msg #konversation Nova različica Konvija je na spletu!"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:2318
#, no-c-format
msgid "/msg Eisfuchs /me is compiling the Handbook right now."
msgstr "/msg Eisfuchs /me trenutno sestavlja priročnik."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>/smsg </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable></"
"userinput> <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>/smsg </command><replaceable>nick|kanal</replaceable></"
"userinput> <userinput><replaceable>sporočilo</replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Same as <userinput><command>/msg</command></userinput> except the message is "
"not displayed on your screen. This is useful for preventing passwords and "
"other sensitive information from remaining exposed on your screen or being "
"logged."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot <userinput><command>/msg</command></userinput> le da sporočilo ni "
"prikazano na vašem zaslonu. To je uporabno, če želite preprečiti, da bi "
"gesla in druge občutljive informacije ostale izpostavljene na vašem zaslonu "
"ali bile zabeležene."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>/amsg </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable></"
"userinput> <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>/amsg </command><replaceable>nick|kanal</replaceable></"
"userinput> <userinput><replaceable>sporočilo</replaceable></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like the <userinput><command>/msg</command></userinput> command above except "
"that the message is sent to all the channels and queries you have open on "
"all the servers you have connected in &konversation;."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot zgornji ukaz <userinput><command>/msg</command></userinput>, le da "
"je sporočilo poslano vsem kanalom in poizvedbam, ki ste jih odprli na vseh "
"strežnikih, ki ste jih povezali v &konversation;."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/op </command> <replaceable>nick</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/op </command> <replaceable>nick</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When entered into a channel tab, attempts to give "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> operator privilege "
"for the channel. May not work if you lack sufficient privilege in the "
"channel (you must be a channel operator yourself). You may enter more than "
"one &i18n-nickname; separated by spaces."
msgstr ""
"Ko vstopi na zavihek kanala, poskuša dati <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> privilegij operaterja za kanal. Morda ne bo "
"delovalo, če nimate dovolj privilegijev na kanalu (sami morate biti operater "
"kanala). Vnesete lahko več kot en &i18n-nickname; ločene s presledki."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/deop </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/deop </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When entered into a channel tab, takes away channel operator privilege from "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput>. You may enter more "
"than one &i18n-nickname; separated by spaces."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete v zavihek kanala, odvzame privilegij operaterja kanala "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput>. Vnesete lahko več "
"kot en &i18n-nickname; ločen s presledki."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2352
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/oper </command><replaceable>[nick]</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/oper </command><replaceable>[nick]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Grants the user with &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> &irc;-Op (Administrator) privilege. This only works "
"if the &i18n-nickname; is listed in the server's O: line. &irc;-Ops have the "
"privilege to <userinput><command>/kill</command></userinput> &i18n-nickname;"
"s, <userinput><command>/connect</command></userinput> servers to the &irc; "
"network, and more. If <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> "
"is not entered, attempts to grant yourself &irc;-Op privilege. You will be "
"prompted for your &irc;-Op user name and password in either case."
msgstr ""
"Dodeli uporabniku z &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>vzdevkom</"
"replaceable></userinput> &irc;-Op (skrbniški) privilegij. To deluje le, če "
"je &i18n-nickname; je naveden v vrstici O: strežnika. &irc;-Ops imajo "
"privilegij za <userinput><command>/kill</command></userinput> &i18n-nickname;"
"<userinput><command>/connect</command></userinput> strežnike z &irc; omrežje "
"in več. Če <userinput><replaceable>vzdevek</replaceable></userinput> ni "
"vnesen, si poskuša dodeliti privilegij &irc;-Op. V obeh primerih boste "
"morali vnesti svoje uporabniško ime &irc;-Op. in geslo."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2361
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/voice </command> <replaceable>nick</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/voice </command> <replaceable>nick</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In certain channels (with +m flag), users cannot send messages unless they "
"have voice privilege. This command attempts to give "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> voice privilege. You "
"must have channel operator privilege to execute this command. This command "
"is mostly used when you are an operator for a moderated channel."
msgstr ""
"Na določenih kanalih (z oznako +m) uporabniki ne morejo pošiljati sporočil, "
"razen če imajo glasovne pravice. Ta ukaz poskuša "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> dati glasovni "
"privilegij. Za izvedbo tega ukaza morate imeti privilegij kanalskega "
"operaterja. Ta ukaz se večinoma uporablja, ko ste operater moderiranega "
"kanala."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2369
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/unvoice </command> <replaceable>nick</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/unvoice </command> <replaceable>nick</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Takes away voice privilege from <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></"
"userinput> in the channel."
msgstr ""
"Odvzema glasovne pravice <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></"
"userinput> v kanalu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/topic </command><replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[message]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/topic </command><replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[message]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attempts to set the topic of <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></"
"userinput> to <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput>. "
"When entered in a channel tab, <userinput><replaceable>channel</"
"replaceable></userinput> may be omitted and defaults to the channel active "
"in the tab. If <userinput><replaceable>message</replaceable></userinput> is "
"omitted, displays the current topic of the channel. Changing a channel topic "
"may fail if you lack sufficient privilege."
msgstr ""
"Poskuša nastaviti temo <userinput><replaceable>kanala</replaceable></"
"userinput> na <userinput><replaceable>sporočilo</replaceable></userinput>. "
"Ko ga vnesete na zavihek kanala, je <userinput><replaceable>kanal</"
"replaceable></userinput> morda izpuščen in privzeto nastavljen na kanal, ki "
"je aktiven na zavihku. Če je <userinput><replaceable>sporočilo</"
"replaceable></userinput> izpuščeno, prikaže trenutno temo kanala. "
"Spreminjanje teme kanala morda ne bo uspelo, če nimate dovolj privilegijev."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/away </command> <replaceable>reason</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/away </command> <replaceable>reason</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If anyone tries to send you a private message or invite you to a channel, "
"they will be told that you are away from your workstation for "
"<userinput><replaceable>reason</replaceable></userinput>. To change your "
"state back to normal, enter <userinput><command>/away</command></userinput> "
"without a <userinput><replaceable>reason</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Če vam kdo poskuša poslati zasebno sporočilo ali vas povabiti na kanal, bo "
"obveščen, da vas ni na vaši delovni postaji zaradi "
"<userinput><replaceable>razloga</replaceable></userinput>. Če želite "
"spremeniti svoje stanje nazaj v običajno, vnesite <userinput><command>/away</"
"command></userinput> brez <userinput><replaceable>razloga</replaceable></"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/aaway </command><replaceable>reason</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/aaway </command><replaceable>razlog</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like the <userinput><command>/away</command></userinput> command above "
"except that the command is sent to all the servers you have connected in "
"&konversation;."
msgstr ""
"Kot zgornji ukaz <userinput><command>/away</command></userinput>, le da je "
"ukaz poslan vsem strežnikom, ki ste jih povezali v &konversation;."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/invite </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[channel]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/invite </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[kanal]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invites the user with &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> to join <userinput><replaceable>channel</"
"replaceable></userinput>. This command is especially useful if the channel "
"is invite-only. When entered in a channel tab, "
"<userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput> may be omitted."
msgstr ""
"Povabi uporabnika z &i18n-nickname;  <userinput><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable></userinput> za pridružitev <userinput><replaceable>kanalu</"
"replaceable></userinput>. Ta ukaz je še posebej uporaben, če je kanal na "
"voljo samo za povabila. Ko ga vnesete na zavihek kanala, je "
"<userinput><replaceable>kanal</replaceable></userinput> morda izpuščen."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command><replaceable>script</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[parameters]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command><replaceable>skript</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[parametri]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes the &konversation;-compatible shell script named "
"<userinput><replaceable>script</replaceable></userinput>, passing it "
"<userinput><replaceable>parameters</replaceable></userinput>. See <link "
"linkend=\"scripting\">Scripting</link> for more information on using and "
"writing scripts."
msgstr ""
"Izvede lupinski skript, združljiv z &konversation;, imenovan "
"<userinput><replaceable>script</replaceable></userinput>, ki mu posreduje "
"<userinput><replaceable>parametre</replaceable></userinput>. Glejte <link "
"linkend=\"scripting\">Skriptiranje</link> za več informacij o uporabi in "
"pisanju skriptov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:2406 index.docbook:2560
#, no-c-format
msgid "/sayversion"
msgstr "/sayversion"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends your system's &konversation;, &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; and &plasma; "
"version numbers to the channel."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje vaš sistem &konversation;, &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; in &plasma; "
"številke različice kanala."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: index.docbook:2410 index.docbook:2564
#, no-c-format
msgid "/exec cmd uname -a"
msgstr "/exec cmd uname -a"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends your &Linux; version string (the output of <quote>uname -a</quote>) to "
"the channel."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje vaš &Linux; niz različice (izhod <quote>uname -a</quote>) v kanal."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2418
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/notify </command><replaceable>[nick]</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/notify </command><replaceable>[nick]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds or removes <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> from "
"your <link linkend=\"nicksonline\">Watched Nicks</link> list. If the &i18n-"
"nickname; is already in the list, it is removed. If it is not in the list, "
"it is added. If <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> is "
"omitted, displays the current list of watched &i18n-nickname;s."
msgstr ""
"Doda ali odstrani <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> z "
"vašega seznama <link linkend=\"nicksonline\">Opazovanih vzdevkov</link>. Če "
"je &i18n-nickname; že na seznamu, je odstranjen. Če ga ni na seznamu, se "
"doda. Če je <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> izpuščen, "
"prikaže trenutni seznam opazovanih &i18n-nickname;"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/kick </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>reason</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/kick </command><replaceable>nick</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>razlog</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When entered in a channel tab, attempts to kick the user with &i18n-"
"nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> from the "
"channel with <userinput><replaceable>reason</replaceable></userinput>. If "
"<userinput><replaceable>reason</replaceable></userinput> is not entered, "
"defaults to the reason in the <link linkend=\"identity\">Settings</link>. "
"This command may only be used in a channel tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko vstopi v zavihek kanala, poskuša brcniti uporabnika z &i18n-nickname; "
"<userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> iz kanala z "
"<userinput><replaceable>razlogom</replaceable></userinput>. Če "
"<userinput><replaceable>razlog</replaceable></userinput> ni vnesen, je "
"privzeto nastavljen razlog v <link linkend=\"identity\">Nastavitve</link>. "
"Ta ukaz se lahko uporablja samo na zavihku kanala."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/ban </command> [<command>-host</command>|<command>-domain</"
"command>| <command>-userhost</command>|<command>-userdomain</command>] "
"<replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> <replaceable>user</replaceable>|"
"<replaceable>mask</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/ban </command> [<command>-host</command>|<command>-domain</"
"command>| <command>-userhost</command>|<command>-userdomain</command>] "
"<replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> <replaceable>user</replaceable>|"
"<replaceable>mask</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attempts to ban the <userinput><replaceable>user</replaceable></userinput> "
"or <userinput><replaceable>mask</replaceable></userinput> from "
"<userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput>. When entered in a "
"channel tab, <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput> may "
"be omitted. For more information on hosts, domains, and masks, see the "
"documents at <ulink url=\"https://www.irchelp.org/\">irchelp.org</ulink>. To "
"get the current ban list for a channel, enter <userinput><command>/mode </"
"command><replaceable>channel</replaceable> <command>b</command></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Poskuša prepovedati <userinput><replaceable>uporabnika</replaceable></"
"userinput> ali <userinput><replaceable>maske</replaceable></userinput> iz "
"<userinput><replaceable>kanala</replaceable></userinput >. Ko ga vnesete na "
"zavihek kanala, je <userinput><replaceable>kanal</replaceable></userinput> "
"morda izpuščen. Za več informacij o gostiteljih, domenah in maskah si "
"oglejte dokumente na <ulink url=\"https://www.irchelp.org/\">irchelp.org</"
"ulink>. Če želite pridobiti trenutni seznam prepovedi za kanal, vnesite "
"<userinput><command>/mode </command><replaceable>kanal</replaceable> "
"<command>b</command></userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/unban </command> <replaceable>[channel]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>pattern</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/unban </command> <replaceable>[kanal]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>vzorec</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reverts a previous banning from a channel. When entered in a channel tab, "
"<userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput> may be omitted."
msgstr ""
"Razveljavi prejšnjo prepoved kanala. Ko ga vnesete na zavihek kanala, je "
"<userinput><replaceable>kanal</replaceable></userinput> morda izpuščen."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/ignore </command> [<command>-all</command>] <replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/ignore </command> [<command>-all</command>] <replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adds <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> to your Ignore "
"list. You may specify more than one &i18n-nickname; separated by spaces. "
"Channel messages from users on your Ignore list are not displayed. In "
"addition, if you enter <userinput><command>-all</command></userinput>, all "
"message types (queries, notices, &CTCP;, DCC, and Exceptions) from the user "
"are ignored as well as channel messages."
msgstr ""
"Doda <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> na vaš seznam "
"prezrtih. Določite lahko več kot en &i18n-nickname; ločeni s presledki. "
"Sporočila kanala uporabnikov na vašem seznamu prezrtih niso prikazana. Poleg "
"tega, če vnesete <userinput><command>-all</command></userinput>, so vse "
"vrste sporočil (poizvedbe, obvestila, &CTCP;, DCC in izjeme) od uporabnika "
"prezrte, kot tudi sporočila kanala."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2463
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/quote </command> <replaceable>cmd</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/quote </command> <replaceable>cmd</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends <userinput><replaceable>cmd</replaceable></userinput> to the server."
msgstr ""
"Strežniku pošlje <userinput><replaceable>cmd</replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2469
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/say </command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/say </command> <replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When entered in a channel tab, sends <userinput><replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable></userinput> to the channel. This is the same as entering "
"<userinput><replaceable>msg</replaceable></userinput> in the channel "
"<interface>Input Line</interface>. Useful for sending &irc; commands when "
"you don't want to execute the command. Two command characters (//) in a row "
"does the same thing as <userinput><command>/say</command></userinput>. Also "
"used by <link linkend=\"scripting\">scripts</link> to send messages."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete na zavihek kanala, kanalu pošlje <userinput><replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable></userinput>. To je enako kot vnos <userinput><replaceable>msg</"
"replaceable></userinput> v kanal <interface>Input Line</interface>. Uporabno "
"za pošiljanje &irc; ukazov, ko ukaza ne želite izvesti. Dva ukazna znaka "
"(//) v vrsti naredita isto kot <userinput><command>/say</command></"
"userinput>. Uporabljajo ga tudi <link linkend=\"scripting\">skripti</link> "
"za pošiljanje sporočil."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/raw </command> [<command>open</command>|<command>close</command>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/raw </command> [<command>open</command>|<command>close</command>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Places the server log in raw mode (<command>open</command>) or stops raw "
"mode (<command>close</command>). If neither <command>open</command> or "
"<command>close</command> is entered, defaults to <command>open</command>. In "
"raw mode, the log displays every message received from the server in native "
"&irc; format."
msgstr ""
"Postavi dnevnik strežnika v neobdelani način (<command>open</command>) ali "
"ustavi surovi način (<command>close</command>). Če ni vnesen niti ukaz "
"<command>open</command> niti <command>close</command>, je privzeto "
"<command>open</command>. V surovem načinu dnevnik prikaže vsako sporočilo, "
"prejeto s strežnika v izvirnem &irc; formatu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new tab running a &konsole;."
msgstr "Odpre nov zavihek, v katerem se izvaja &konsole;."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/server </command> <replaceable>[url]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[pwd]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/server </command> <replaceable>[url]</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>[pwd]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Connects to the server at address <userinput><replaceable>url</replaceable></"
"userinput>. If <userinput><replaceable>url</replaceable></userinput> is "
"omitted, connects to the server associated with the tab where you enter the "
"command. This is useful for re-connecting to a server when disconnected. If "
"the server requires a password in order to connect to it, enter it for "
"<userinput><replaceable>pwd</replaceable></userinput>. If the server "
"requires a port number other than the default (6667), enter the "
"<userinput><replaceable>url</replaceable></userinput> like this: "
"<replaceable>irc.kde.org:6665</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Povezuje se s strežnikom na naslovu <userinput><replaceable>url</"
"replaceable></userinput>. Če je <userinput><replaceable>url</replaceable></"
"userinput> izpuščen, se poveže s strežnikom, povezanim z zavihkom, kjer "
"vnesete ukaz. To je uporabno za ponovno povezavo s strežnikom, ko je "
"povezava prekinjena. Če strežnik zahteva geslo za povezavo z njim, ga "
"vnesite za <userinput><replaceable>pwd</replaceable></userinput>. Če "
"strežnik zahteva številko vrat, ki ni privzeta (6667), vnesite "
"<userinput><replaceable>url</replaceable></userinput> takole: "
"<replaceable>irc.kde.org:6665</replaceable>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/dcc </command> <command>SEND </command><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable> <replaceable>[filename]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/dcc </command> <command>SEND </command><replaceable>nick</"
"replaceable> <replaceable>[filename]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends <userinput><replaceable>filename</replaceable></userinput> to the user "
"with &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput>. "
"If <userinput><replaceable>filename</replaceable></userinput> is omitted, a "
"dialog appears for you to select a file."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje <userinput><replaceable>ime datoteke</replaceable></userinput> "
"uporabniku z &i18n-nickname; <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></"
"userinput>. Če je <userinput><replaceable>ime datoteke</replaceable></"
"userinput> izpuščeno, se prikaže pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the <guilabel>DCC Status</guilabel> tab."
msgstr "Odpre zavihek <guilabel>Status DCC</guilabel>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/ctcp </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable> "
"<command>ping</command>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/ctcp </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable> "
"<command>ping</command>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends a PING message to <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></"
"userinput> or <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput>. "
"This is useful for determining if someone you are talking with has a high "
"network lag, or (when sent to a channel) if your system has a high lag."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje sporočilo PING na <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></"
"userinput> ali <userinput><replaceable>kanal</replaceable></userinput>. To "
"je uporabno za ugotavljanje, ali ima nekdo, s katerim se pogovarjate, visoko "
"omrežno zakasnitev ali (ko je poslano na kanal), ali ima vaš sistem veliko "
"zakasnitev."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/ctcp </command><replaceable>nick|channel</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>msg</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/ctcp </command><replaceable>nick|kanal</replaceable> "
"<replaceable>msg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends a message to <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> or "
"all users in <userinput><replaceable>channel</replaceable></userinput>. This "
"is similar to the <userinput><command>/msg</command></userinput> command "
"above, except that the message is sent using the &CTCP; protocol. The "
"response on the other end depends on the &irc; client program the user is "
"running. For example, when conversing with another &konversation; user, "
"<userinput><replaceable>/ctcp Eisfuchs TIME</replaceable></userinput> will "
"return the system time on Eisfuch's computer. <userinput><replaceable>/ctcp "
"Eisfuchs VERSION</replaceable></userinput> will return the &konversation; "
"version number from Eisfuch's computer."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje sporočilo <userinput><replaceable>nick</replaceable></userinput> ali "
"vsem uporabnikom v <userinput><replaceable>kanalu</replaceable></userinput>. "
"To je podobno zgornjemu ukazu <userinput><command>/msg</command></"
"userinput>, le da je sporočilo poslano z uporabo &CTCP; protokola. Odgovor "
"na drugi strani je odvisen od &irc; odjemalskega programa, ki ga izvaja "
"uporabnik. Na primer, ko se pogovarjate z drugim uporabnikom &konversation;, "
"bo <userinput><replaceable>/ctcp Eisfuchs TIME</replaceable></userinput> "
"vrnil sistemski čas na Eisfuchovem računalniku. <userinput><replaceable>/"
"ctcp Eisfuchs VERSION</replaceable></userinput> bo vrnil številko različice "
"&konversation; iz Eisfuchovega računalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting"
msgstr "Skriptiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; comes with some handy scripts you can run from the program. "
"To run a script, in a channel, query, DCC, or server tab, type a command of "
"the form"
msgstr ""
"&konversation; vsebuje nekaj priročnih skriptov, ki jih lahko zaženete iz "
"programa. Če želite zagnati skript, v zavihku kanala, poizvedbe, DCC ali "
"strežnika vnesite ukaz obrazca"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>script</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>parameters</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>skript</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>parametri</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"which executes the script named <userinput><replaceable>script</"
"replaceable></userinput> passing it (optional) "
"<userinput><replaceable>parameters</replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"ki izvede skript z imenom <userinput><replaceable>script</replaceable></"
"userinput> in mu posreduje (neobvezno) <userinput><replaceable>parametre</"
"replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2558
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example, type the following command in a channel tab"
msgstr "Na primer, v zavihek kanala vnesite naslednji ukaz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"to send your &konversation;, &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; and &plasma; version "
"numbers to the channel."
msgstr ""
"za pošiljanje vaših &konversation;, &Qt;, &kde-frameworks; in &plasma; "
"številke različice kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"executes the <userinput><replaceable>cmd</replaceable></userinput> script, "
"passing it <userinput><replaceable>uname -a</replaceable></userinput>. This "
"sends your &Linux; version string to the channel."
msgstr ""
"izvede skript <userinput><replaceable>cmd</replaceable></userinput> in mu "
"posreduje <userinput><replaceable>uname -a</replaceable></userinput>. To "
"pošlje vaš &Linux; niz različice v kanal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To learn more about the scripts installed with &konversation; please see the "
"<link linkend=\"scripts_ref\">Script Reference Guide</link>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvedeti več o skriptih, nameščenih s &konversation; glejte <link "
"linkend=\"scripts_ref\">Referenčni vodnik po skriptih</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a list of all available scripts, type the following command in a "
"&konversation; screen."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dobiti seznam vseh razpoložljivih skriptov, vnesite naslednji ukaz "
"na &konversation; zaslon."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2576
#, no-c-format
msgid "/exec --showpath media"
msgstr "/exec --showpath media"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Then browse to folder from the output to see the list."
msgstr "Nato poiščite mapo iz izhoda, da si ogledate seznam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can write your own scripts. Scripts are shell scripts and can be written "
"in any shell language, such as bash, perl, or python. When &konversation; "
"runs a script, the first two parameters sent to the script are:"
msgstr ""
"Lahko pišete svoje lastne skripte. Skripti so lupinski skripti in jih je "
"mogoče napisati v katerem koli lupinskem jeziku, kot je bash, perl ali "
"python. Ko &konversation; zažene skript, sta prva dva parametra, poslana "
"skriptu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2586
#, no-c-format
msgid "The address of the server."
msgstr "Naslov strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2588
#, no-c-format
msgid "The channel name."
msgstr "Ime kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a sample shell script (cmd)."
msgstr "Tukaj je vzorčni skript lupine (cmd)."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:2595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"#!/bin/sh\n"
"\n"
"# Executes a command and prints the output into Konversation.\n"
"\n"
"SERVER=$1;\n"
"TARGET=$2;\n"
"shift;shift;\n"
"\n"
"$@ | while read line; do qdbus org.kde.konversation /irc say $SERVER "
"\"$TARGET\" \"$@: $line\"; done"
msgstr ""
"#!/bin/sh\n"
"\n"
"# Executes a command and prints the output into Konversation.\n"
"\n"
"SERVER=$1;\n"
"TARGET=$2;\n"
"shift;shift;\n"
"\n"
"$@ | while read line; do qdbus org.kde.konversation /irc say $SERVER "
"\"$TARGET\" \"$@: $line\"; done"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that the script uses qdbus to communicate with &konversation;. The "
"<computeroutput>say</computeroutput> command causes the output to be sent to "
"the channel as a normal message. To display something in the tab without "
"sending it to other users, use <computeroutput>info</computeroutput> "
"instead. Look at the existing script files for more examples of writing "
"scripts."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da skript uporablja qdbus za komunikacijo s &konversation;. "
"Ukaz <computeroutput>say</computeroutput> povzroči, da se izhod pošlje "
"kanalu kot običajno sporočilo. Če želite nekaj prikazati na zavihku, ne da "
"bi to poslali drugim uporabnikom, namesto tega uporabite "
"<computeroutput>info</computeroutput>. Oglejte si obstoječe skriptne "
"datoteke za več primerov pisanja skriptov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be able to run a script you have written, you must install it by copying "
"it to <filename class=\"directory\">$(qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation)/"
"konversation/scripts</filename>. You must also give the file execute "
"privilege, for example <userinput><replaceable>chmod a+x myscript</"
"replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zagnati skript, ki ste ga napisali, ga morate namestiti tako, da "
"ga kopirate v <filename class=\"directory\">$(qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation)/konversation/scripts</filename>. Datoteki morate dati "
"tudi privilegij za izvajanje, na primer <userinput><replaceable>chmod a+x "
"myscript</replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Reference Guide"
msgstr "Referenčni vodnik za skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; comes with several scripts installed by default, please refer "
"to this guide to learn how to use them."
msgstr ""
"&konversation; prihaja z več skripti, ki so privzeto nameščeni, glejte ta "
"priročnik, če želite izvedeti, kako jih uporabljati."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>bug</replaceable> [<replaceable>Bug "
"Number|Search String</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>bug</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>Številka hrošča|Iskalni niz</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script is used to open your browser to search for the given string or "
"bug number on <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde;'s Bugzilla</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ta skript se uporablja za odpiranje vašega brskalnika za iskanje danega niza "
"ali številke hrošča na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde;'s "
"Bugzilla</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: To open your browser to search for bug 123456"
msgstr "Primer: Če želite odpreti brskalnik za iskanje napake 123456"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2620
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>bug 123456</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>bug 123456</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample action: The default browser in your &systemsettings; should open to "
"<replaceable>https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=123456</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"Primer dejanja: Privzeti brskalnik v &systemsettings; naj se odpre na "
"<replaceable>https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=123456</replaceable>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>cmd</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>command line arguments</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>cmd</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>argumenti ukazne vrstice</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script is used to have the output of the command line arguments to be "
"written to your current channel."
msgstr ""
"Ta skript se uporablja za pisanje argumentov ukazne vrstice v vašem "
"trenutnem kanalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Example: To show everyone in your current channel what version of "
"&konversation; you have installed."
msgstr ""
"Primer: Če želite vsem v vašem trenutnem kanalu pokazati, katero različico "
"&konversation; ste namestili."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>cmd konversation --version</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>cmd konversation --version</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sample output: <replaceable>Konversation: 1.6</replaceable>"
msgstr "Vzorec izpisa: <replaceable>Konversation: 1.6</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"WARNING! The output of the entire command is posted to everyone in the "
"current channel tab! Please use with care."
msgstr ""
"OPOZORILO! Izhod celotnega ukaza je objavljen vsem na trenutnem zavihku "
"kanala! Prosimo, uporabljajte previdno."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2638 index.docbook:2643
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>fortune</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>fortune</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2641
#, no-c-format
msgid "This script when run will output a Random Fortune."
msgstr "Ta skript, ko se zažene, izpiše naključno bogastvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: To output a random fortune to your current channel tab."
msgstr ""
"Primer: Za izpis naključnega bogastva na zavihku vašega trenutnega kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample output: <replaceable>Random Fortune: Never make any mistaeks. -- "
"Anonymous, in a mail discussion about to a kernel bug report</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"Vzorec izpisa: <replaceable>Random Fortune: Nikoli ne delajte nobenih napak. "
"-- Anonimno, v e-poštni razpravi o poročilu o napaki v jedru</replaceable>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>gauge</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>percentage</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>gauge</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>odstotek</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script shows a simple text based progress bar for the given percentage."
msgstr ""
"Ta skript prikazuje preprosto besedilno vrstico napredka za podani odstotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Example: To output a progress bar with 50% completion to the current channel "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Primer: Za prikaz vrstice napredka s 50-odstotno dokončanostjo na zavihku "
"trenutnega kanala."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>gauge 50</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>gauge 50</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sample output: <replaceable>Beer load [ | ] 50%</replaceable>"
msgstr "Vzorec izpisa: <replaceable>Beer load [ | ] 50 %</replaceable>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>media</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>audio|video|{player}</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>media</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>avdio|video|{player}</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a Now Playing script for various media players. It also features a "
"method to show Now Playing information for only audio players, or only video "
"players via the optional command arguments <replaceable>audio</replaceable> "
"and <replaceable>video</replaceable>. Additionally, it's possible to specify "
"the media player you wish to query."
msgstr ""
"To je skript Now Playing za različne medijske predvajalnike. Vsebuje tudi "
"metodo za prikaz informacij o tem, ki se trenutno predvajajo, samo za "
"predvajalnike zvoka ali samo predvajalnike videa prek izbirnih ukaznih "
"argumentov <replaceable>avdio</replaceable> in <replaceable>video</"
"replaceable>. Poleg tega je mogoče določiti predstavnostni predvajalnik, ki "
"ga želite poizvedovati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following media players are supported: Amarok (audio), JuK (audio), "
"Kaffeine (video, audio), KMPlayer (video, audio), KPlayer (video, audio), "
"kdetv (video), Yammi (audio), Audacious (audio), MPD (audio)."
msgstr ""
"Podprti so naslednji medijski predvajalniki: Amarok (avdio), JuK (avdio), "
"Kaffeine (video, avdio), KMPlayer (video, avdio), KPlayer (video, avdio), "
"kdetv (video), Yammi (avdio), Audacious ( avdio), MPD (avdio)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2669
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: To output your currently playing song in Amarok."
msgstr "Primer: Za izpis vaše trenutno predvajane pesmi v Amaroku."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2670
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>media amarok</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>media amarok</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample output: <replaceable>* user is listening to You Give Love A Bad Name "
"by Bon Jovi on Slippery When Wet [Amarok]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"Primer izhoda: <replaceable>* uporabnik posluša You Give Love A Bad Name "
"skupine Bon Jovi na Slippery When Wet [Amarok]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2688 index.docbook:2694
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>sysinfo</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>sysinfo</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script outputs some detailed information about your system by combining "
"the outputs of several commands and formatting them appropriately."
msgstr ""
"Ta skript prikaže nekaj podrobnih informacij o vašem sistemu tako, da združi "
"rezultate več ukazov in jih ustrezno oblikuje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Example: To output some information about your system to the current channel "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Primer: Za izpis nekaterih informacij o vašem sistemu na zavihku trenutnega "
"kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample output: <replaceable>Sysinfo for 'user-desktop': Running inside KDE "
"Plasma 5.6.5 on Ubuntu 16.04.1 LTS (Xenial Xerus) powered by Linux 4.4.0-47-"
"generic, CPU: Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-4910MQ CPU @ 2.90GHz at 2996-3338/3900 "
"MHz, RAM: 15795/15967 MB, Storage: 1591/2281 GB, 406 procs, 47.59h up</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"Vzorčni izhod: <replaceable>Sysinfo for 'user-desktop': Running inside KDE "
"Plasma 5.6.5 on Ubuntu 16.04.1 LTS (Xenial Xerus) powered by Linux 4.4.0-47-"
"generic, CPU: Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-4910MQ CPU @ 2.90GHz at 2996-3338/3900 "
"MHz, RAM: 15795/15967 MB, Storage: 1591/2281 GB, 406 procs, 47.59h up</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>tinyurl</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>Link Address</replaceable>]"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>tinyurl</replaceable> "
"[<replaceable>Naslov povezave</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script uses Tinyurl's api to turn the given link into a tinyurl that is "
"then sent to the current channel tab."
msgstr ""
"Ta skript uporablja Tinyurlov API za pretvorbo dane povezave v tinyurl, ki "
"se nato pošlje na zavihek trenutnega kanala."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: To give someone a short link to https://konversation.kde.org"
msgstr "Primer: nekomu dati kratko povezavo do https://konversation.kde.org"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>tinyurl https://konversation.kde.org</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>tinyurl https://konversation.kde.org</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2706
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sample output: <replaceable>https://tinyurl.com/y4rk8wa3</replaceable>"
