msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Okno</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri dnevniško datoteko za</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a screen with the log of messages from the current tab. Only works "
"for <interface>Channel</interface>, <interface>Server Messages</interface>, "
"and <interface>Query</interface> tabs. Logging must be enabled in "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Settings</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Configure "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Behavior</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Logging</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> on the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže zaslon z dnevnikom sporočil s trenutnega zavihka. Deluje samo za "
"zavihke <interface>Kanal</interface>, <interface>Server Messages</interface> "
"in <interface>Query</interface>. Beleženje mora biti omogočeno v "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Nastavitve</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj "
"Konversation</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Vedenje</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Beleženje</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> v glavnem meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konversation; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for "
"more information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&konversation; ima skupno &kde; Element menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za "
"več informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I start &konversation;, I'd like to connect to a server without joining "
"any channels. How do I do that?"
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženem &konversation;, bi se rad povezal s strežnikom, ne da bi se "
"pridružil kanalom. Kako to naredim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Edit Server</link> screen, "
"leave the <guilabel>Channels</guilabel> frame empty."
msgstr ""
"Na zaslonu <link linkend=\"serverlist-addnetwork\">Urejanje strežnika</link> "
"pustite okvir <guilabel>Kanali</guilabel> prazen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konversation; won't connect to any servers. What is wrong?"
msgstr "&konversation; se ne bo povezal z nobenim strežnikom. Kaj je narobe?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3212
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are several things that could be wrong."
msgstr "Obstaja več stvari, ki bi lahko bile narobe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that you have entered the correct <guilabel>Server name</guilabel> "
"and the correct <guilabel>Port</guilabel> in the <link linkend=\"serverlist-"
"addserver\">Add Server</link> screen."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da ste vnesli pravilno <guilabel>Ime strežnika</guilabel> in "
"pravilna <guilabel>Vrata</guilabel> na zaslonu <link linkend=\"serverlist-"
"addserver\">Dodaj strežnik</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the output in the <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Server "
"Messages</link> screen for any error messages. Did the server reject the "
"connection because of a bad password? Did the server reject the connection "
"because it requires <acronym>IDENTD</acronym> and your computer did not "
"respond to the <acronym>IDENT</acronym> request? Did you check the SSL "
"protocol box but the server does not support SSL?"
msgstr ""
"Preverite izpis na zaslonu <link linkend=\"channel-screen-tour\">Sporočila "
"strežnika</link> za morebitna sporočila o napakah. Ali je strežnik zavrnil "
"povezavo zaradi slabega gesla? Ali je strežnik zavrnil povezavo, ker zahteva "
"<acronym>IDENTD</acronym>, vaš računalnik pa se ni odzval na zahtevo "
"<acronym>IDENT</acronym>? Ali ste označili polje za protokol SSL, vendar "
"strežnik ne podpira SSL?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are behind a firewall, make sure the correct ports are enabled. "
"&konversation; needs the following ports enabled:"
msgstr ""
"Če ste za požarnim zidom, se prepričajte, da so omogočena pravilna vrata. "
"&konversation; potrebuje naslednja vrata omogočena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outgoing TCP 6667 (or the port of the server you connect to)"
msgstr "Odhodni TCP 6667 (ali vrata strežnika, s katerim se povezujete)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Incoming TCP 113 (if the server requires IDENTD)"
msgstr "Dohodni TCP 113 (če strežnik zahteva IDENTD)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on &irc; connection problems, see <ulink url=\"https://"
"github.com/irchelp/wio/blob/gh-pages/networks/connectprob.md\">irchelp.org</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o &irc; težave s povezavo, glejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"github.com/irchelp/wio/blob/gh-pages/networks/connectprob.md\">irchelp.org</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I go to <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel "
"List</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>, I cannot select it. Why is that?"
msgstr ""
"Ko grem v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Okno</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Seznam kanalov</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice>, ga ne morem izbrati. Zakaj?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Channel List</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> menu entry will be grayed-out if a non-channel "
"tab, &eg; <guilabel>Watched Nicks</guilabel>, is currently being viewed. To "
"make it selectable again go back to a channel tab or the server tab."
msgstr ""
"Vnos v meniju <menuchoice> <guimenu>Okno</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Seznam "
"kanalov</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> bo zatemnjen, če bo zavihek, ki ni kanal, "
"&eg;. <guilabel>Opazovani vzdevki</guilabel>, je trenutno v ogledu. Če ga "
"želite znova izbrati, se vrnite na zavihek kanala ali zavihek strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I have &konversation; automatically mark me as away after a period of "
"inactivity?"
msgstr ""
"Kako imam oznako odsoten, da me &konversation; samodejno označi kot odsoten "
"po obdobju nedejavnosti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Auto-away messages are configured on a per-identity basis. To enable auto-"
"away select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Identities</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Choose the identity for which you want to enable "
"auto-away from the drop down list at the top of the dialog and go to the "
"<guilabel>Away</guilabel> tab. Check the <guilabel>Automatic Away</guilabel> "
"option."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila o samodejni odsotnosti so konfigurirana glede na identiteto. Če "
"želite omogočiti samodejno odsotnost, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Identitete</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na spustnem seznamu na vrhu pogovornega okna "
"izberite identiteto, za katero želite omogočiti samodejno odsotnost, in "
"pojdite na zavihek <guilabel>Zdoma</guilabel>. Preverite možnost "
"<guilabel>Samodejna odsotnost</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How to avoid the <guilabel>Auto Replace</guilabel> feature of the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface>?"
msgstr ""
"Kako se izogniti funkciji <guilabel>Samodejna zamenjava</guilabel> vmesnika "
"<interface>Vnosna vrstica</interface>?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> instead of just "
"&Enter; to avoid parsing and automatically replacing the text in the "
"<interface>Input Line</interface> according to the options in the settings "
"dialog page <menuchoice><guimenu>Behavior</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Auto "
"Replace</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> namesto samo "
"&Enter; da se izognete razčlenjevanju in samodejni zamenjavi besedila v "
"<interface>Vnosni vrstici</interface> glede na možnosti na strani "
"pogovornega okna z nastavitvami <menuchoice><guimenu>Vedenje</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Samodejna zamenjava</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Where can I find the scripts included with &konversation;?"
msgstr "Kje lahko najdem skripte, vključene v &konversation;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run this command in &konversation;'s input line (using the media script as "
"an example, since it comes with any &konversation; installation):"
msgstr ""
"Zaženite ta ukaz v vnosni vrstici &konversation; (z uporabo medijske skripte "
"kot primera, saj je priložen vsaki namestitvi &konversation;):"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>--showpath media</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>--showpath media</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sample output: <replaceable>The script file 'media' was found at: /usr/share/"
"konversation/scripts/media</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"Vzorčni rezultat: <replaceable>Skriptna datoteka 'media' je bila najdena "
"na: /usr/share/konversation/scripts/media</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3305
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I make my text bold/italicized/underlined?"
msgstr "Kako naredim svoje besedilo krepko/ležeče/podčrtano?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Bbold%B text.</userinput>"
msgstr "Primer: <userinput>To je moje besedilo %Bbold%B.</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3309 index.docbook:3315 index.docbook:3321 index.docbook:3327
#: index.docbook:3333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output:"
msgstr "Izhod:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Iitalicized%I text.</userinput>"
msgstr "Primer: <userinput>To je moje %Iležečed% besedilo.</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Uunderlined%U text.</userinput>"
msgstr "Primer: <userinput>To je moje %Upodčrtano% besedilo.</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Sstruck-out%S text.</userinput>"
msgstr "Primer: <userinput>To je moje %Sprečrtano%S besedilo.</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example: <userinput>This is my %Mmonospace%M text.</userinput>"
msgstr "Primer: <userinput>To je moje %Mmonospace%M besedilo.</userinput>"

